title: How U.S. I-Day parade turned into 'warzone'; Shooter Crimo unleashed AR-15 in Chicago Suburb
description: It was the morning of the U.S. Independence Day Parade celebration for a Chicago suburb when suddenly dozens of bullets were fired, followed by chaos in the streets amid screams. It was at this moment, when 22-year-old Robert Crimo opened fire at the crowd from a rooftop with his AR-15. He was arrested later after hours of manhunt. 6 people died and at least 80 others were injured in the mass shooting, including kids. One of the clips, which is particularly disturbing, captures the moment when the attacker opened fire from a rooftop. People ran in all directions, seeking shelter, and teens - on bicycles - could not understand what was happening. Watch this video for more details.|#unitedstates #massshooting #july4th #illinois #july4 #chicago #independeceday #ar15 #shootout

title: UP: Man who sold chicken on paper with Hindu deities, attacks cops with knife before arrest
description: A Muslim roadside restaurant owner has been arrested in Uttar Pradeshâ€™s Sambhal district for wrapping chicken in a newspaper carrying images of Hindu deities. As per police FIR, when a police team reached his shop, Talib Hussain attacked them with a knife with an intention to kill. He has been booked under IPC Sections 153-A (promoting enmity between different groups on grounds of religion, race, place of birth, residence), 295A (deliberate and malicious acts, intended to outrage religious feelings of any class by insulting its religion or religious beliefs) and 307 (attempt to murder). Workers at the restaurant insisted wrapping food items in newspapers is a common practice and Talib did not do this to hurt anyone. They added it was just a matter of chance that Talib used a newspaper carrying images of Hindu gods and goddesses. Watch this video for more details.|#muslim #chicken #uttarpradesh #sambhal #religion #religious #uppolice

title: Neon White Review
description: Reviewed by Luke Reilly on PC. Also available on Nintendo Switch.||||"Neon White is a quick and compulsive first-person platformer that's surprisingly simple to understand and play, but packs a very stern speedrunning challenge at its core. Tying your combat options to your traversal mechanics, Neon White makes every encounter a deadly parkour puzzle that can be replayed over and over, in search of the perfect run and the tightest time. The dialogue between its unlikeable troupe of angst-ridden, anime-inspired assassins may be a hokey misstep, but its airtight level design and fantastic sense of momentum ensure Neon White's gameplay is something to celebrate."

title: Suspect arrested over US mass shooting at 4 July parade - BBC News
description: US police have arrested a suspect after six people were killed in a mass shooting at an Independence Day parade in Highland Park, Illinois.| |Robert E Crimo III, 22, was detained after a brief chase, police said.| |The gunman climbed on to a roof, shooting randomly at spectators using a high-powered rifle.| |It is the latest mass shooting to hit the US - there has been one in every week of 2022. President Joe Biden said he was "shocked" by the violence.| |Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: Aksi Penerjun Payung Hingga Berikan Bunga ke Iriana Jokowi pada HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara
description: SEMARANG, KOMPAS.TV  HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara dilangsungkan di Akademi Kepolisian Semarang, Jawa Tengah pada 5 Juli 2022.||||Presiden Jokowi menjadi inspektur upacara di Peringatan HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara ini.||||Sementara itu, sebanyak 41 penerjun payung turun di Lapangan Akpol Semarang. Mereka terdiri dari personel gabungan Polri dan TNI sebagai bentuk sinergitas.||||Para penerjun ini terbang menggunakan pesawat CN295 milik TNI Angkatan Udara.||||Baca Juga 72 Penerjun Payung Korpaskhas Meriahkan HUT TNI AU ke-72 di https://www.kompas.tv/article/22933/72-penerjun-payung-korpaskhas-meriahkan-hut-tni-au-ke-72||||Kapten Penerbang CN295 adalah Kapten Penerbang Jati dan Co-pilot adalah Lettu Penerbang Jones dan Letda Penerbang Andre.||||Para penerbang ini melakukan aksinya dari ketinggian 10 ribu kaki.||||Dalam momen ini juga terlihat penerjun payung wanita memberikan rangkaian bunga kepada Ibu Negara Iriana Jokowi.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305974/aksi-penerjun-payung-hingga-berikan-bunga-ke-iriana-jokowi-pada-hut-ke-76-bhayangkara
tags: TNI Polri|aksi penerjun payung|hut ke-76 bhayangkara|presiden jokowi

title: Parade shooting 'person of interest' in custody
description: A gunman on a rooftop opened fire on an Independence Day parade in suburban Chicago on Monday, killing at least six people, wounding at least 30. Robert Crimo III, described as a 'person of interest' was taken into custody. title: Saat Megawati Kaget Prabowo Beri Hormat di HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara
description: SEMARANG, KOMPAS.TV  Inilah momen di saat Menteri Pertahanan Prabowo Subianto memberi hormat kepada Ketum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri yang terlihat kaget dan tertawa mendapatkan sapaan dari Prabowo Subianto.||||Prabowo dan Megawati hadir dan duduk berdampingan di HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara pada 5 Juli 2022.||||HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara ini diselenggarakan di Semarang, Jawa Tengah.||||Baca Juga Prabowo Puji Keberhasilan Pemerintahan Jokowi di Berbagai Bidang saat Beri Kuliah Umum di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305492/prabowo-puji-keberhasilan-pemerintahan-jokowi-di-berbagai-bidang-saat-beri-kuliah-umum||||Sementara itu, Presiden Jokowi menjadi inspektur upacara di Peringatan HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara di Akademi Kepolisian Semarang, Jawa Tengah.||||Peringatan HUT ke-76 Bhayangkara ini dilangsungkan pada Selasa, 5 Juli 2022.||||Video Editor: : Lintang||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/306018/saat-megawati-kaget-prabowo-beri-hormat-di-hut-ke-76-bhayangkara

title: How local law enforcement agencies work to secure large summer events
description: The shooting at a Fourth of July parade in Highland Park, Ill. has many law enforcement agencies on alert as more summer celebrations continue.  At least six people are dead and dozens more injured after the shooting on Monday morning in the city north of Chicago.  Law enforcement knows that a shooting like this can put people on edge, and they are sharing their plans for security as we move through the summer.

title: MINI VS. GIANT | Cute Fidget Toys Crafts And Ways To Entertain Your Kids
description: Hello there! Do you remember fidget toys trend? Have you already thrown them away? We hope, you haven't. Because they are truly genius and multi-purpose! If your children love pop it things, forget about birthday cake - make a giant birthday lollipop instead! Who needs small number candle when you can't eat it? Make a huge edible number according to your kid's age! Does your son eat color paints, crayons and pencils? Ours are absolutely the same! They can't stop eating any colorful things, so why should we restrict it? Let's make them edible! And if you don't have any fidget toy, go and craft a new one! Take two balloons and fill one with glitter! Trust us, your daughter will be glad to get that gift! ||And if you still want to learn how to deal with awkward parenting situations, you can find a solution in our videos! title: China prepares to give US$140 million parliament building to Zimbabwe
description: Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: |https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube|China is preparing to give Zimbabwe a new US$140 million building that will be home to the African nationâ€™s parliament. The gift is the latest in a series of grand projects across Africa that are designed to deepen Beijingâ€™s influence on the continent where China is already the largest trading partner and lender. The site at Mount Hampden, about 18km (11 miles) northwest of Zimbabweâ€™s capital Harare, heralds the start of a new city. The 650-seat building will replace the current colonial-era structure which has only 100 seats for Zimbabweâ€™s 350 legislators. The new parliament built by Chinaâ€™s Shanghai Construction Group was fully paid for by Beijing. It took 42 months to complete after a 10-month delay caused by Covid-19 disruptions.|Support us:|https://subscribe.scmp.com|Follow us on:|Website:  https://www.scmp.com|Facebook:  https://facebook.com/scmp|Twitter:  https://twitter.com/scmpnews|Instagram:  https://instagram.com/scmpnews|Linkedin:  https://www.linkedin.com/company/south-china-morning-post/|#scmp #World #Zimbabwe

title: Is It Time To Ditch Gender-Neutral Toilets? Concerns About Women's Safety Sparks Debate | GMB
description: Schools, hospitals, theatres and office buildings under construction must include separate lavatories for men and women, government minister Kemi Badenoch has ordered. The legal requirement for developers in England to include gender-specific lavatories comes after schoolchildren were avoiding using gender-neutral lavatories because they did not want to share them with the opposite sex. title: On Cam: Racist slurs hurled at Indian fans during Ind-Eng match at Edgbaston; ECB vows probe
description: Indian fans were subjected to racial abuse during the India-England 4th test match in Edgbaston. This incident came to light after some of the fans took to Twitter and posted photos and videos of the incident. They also claimed that no action was taken despite complaining to the steward about the incident. Meanwhile, the England Cricket Board, reacting to the tweets, apologised for the incident and promised a probe. Edgbaston stadium's chief executive also issued a statement condemning the incident. Watch this video to know more.|#Racism #India #England #Edgbaston #RacialSlur #Abuse #IndianFans #EnglandCricketBoard #Apology

title: Uddhav challenges Maha CM Eknath for mid-term polls; Sena accuses BJP of â€˜stealing majority'
description: The Uddhav Thackeray faction has cried foul after Maharashtra CM eknath Shinde's floor test victory. Through its mouthpiece Saamna, Sena termed Eknath's victory as stolen majority. Separately, Uddhav Thackeray even challenged Eknath Shinde for early mid-term polls. Quoting Uddhav at a meet of district presidents on Monday, PTI reported, â€œThis is BJP's ploy to end the Shiv Sena. Instead of playing all these games, we will go to the court of people. If we are wrong, people of the state will send us home. If you (BJP and Shinde group) are wrong, people will send you home.â€ Watch this video for more information.|#uddhavthackeray #eknathshinde #maharashtra #devendrafadnavis #bjp #shivsena #saamna #polls #midtermelections

title: Rahul fake news: Anchor Rohit Ranjanâ€™s detention sparks UP versus Chhattisgarh police fight
description: Zee News anchor Rohit Ranjan has been detained by the Noida police after he ran a misleading video clip of Rahul Gandhi. He was detained by Noida police this morning after Chhattisgarh cops reached his house to arrest him. He informed Yogi Adityanath & Ghaziabad police via Twitter about Chhattisgarh police's entry. This sparked a massive state police war. On July 1, Rohit in his show ran a misleading clip of Rahul Gandhi linking it to Udaipur's tailor Kanhaiya Lal's murder. After the row, Zee News had apologised for running wrong content. Watch this video to know more.|#RahulGandhi #ZeeNews #RohitRanjan #ZeeMedia #MisleadingClip #Congress #SubhashChandra #FakeNews #YogiAdityanath #UPPolice #ChhattisgarhPolice #BhupeshBaghel #Noida #Ghaziabad #Raipur #UdaipurMurder #KanhaiyaLal

description: Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 |Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu |We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.|About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:|--------------------------------------------------------------------|The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. title: India slams 'disrespect' to Goddess Kali in Canada; Indian HC in Ottawa seeks withdrawal of poster
description: India has asked Canada to withdraw the 'disrespectful' depiction of goddess Kali smoking in a film poster. The Indian High Commission in Ottawa urged Canadian authorities to withdraw 'provocative material'. This is after the Hindu community members accused the filmmaker of disrespecting Hindu gods. Back home, the poster has sparked massive outrage with Hindu groups slamming the filmmaker. title: What is the link between extreme weather and climate change? - BBC News
description: Extreme weather events in Italy, Australia and Japan are believed by many to be linked to man-made climate change.|In the Italian alps, at least seven people have been killed after being caught in an avalanche sparked by the collapse of the Marmolada glacier.|Meanwhile, Australia's largest city Sydney saw torrential rain and flooding, in which a man died and thousands were evacuated.|At the end of June, Japan suffered its worst heatwave ever recorded which saw more than 5,000 across the country hospitalised.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#ClimateChange #Avalanche #BBCNews

title: On Camera, Sidhu Moose Wala Shooters Seen Waving Guns, Celebrating In Car
description: The killers of singer Sidhu Moose Wala are seen celebrating with their weapons, apparently after the crime, in a set of videos found on the phone of one of the shooters. The five men in a car, all of them smiling, are seen flaunting their guns at the camera as Punjabi music blared in the background. Two videos, celebrating the murder, emerged after the phone of the youngest of the shooters, Ankit Sirsa, was scanned. The videos were posted on his now-deleted Instagram handle.|About NDTV: NDTV brings you unbiased and comprehensive coverage of news and entertainment programmes in India and abroad. title: Tak Punya Smartphone, Sopir Angkot Bingung Beli BBM dengan Aplikasi Mypertamina
description: INDRAMAYU, KOMPAS.TV - Tidak punya ponsel pintar, para sopir angkot tolak beli BBM pakai aplikasi atau website Mypertamina.||||Para sopir angkot di Indramayu ini misalnya, menolak penggunanaan Mypertamina.||||Mereka mengaku berat dan ribet jika harus beli pertalite dan solar dengan Mypetamina.||||Para sopir bingung lantaran tidak punya ponsel pintar mumpuni untuk mengikuti ketentuan Pertamina.||||Sebelumnya, pihak Pertamina menjelaskan skema beli BBM lewat Mypertamina agar penyaluran subsidi BBM tepat sasaran.||||Pasalnya selama ini, 60 persen masyarakat yang menggunakan BBM subsidi adalah golongan masyarakat yang mampu. Alias tidak tepat saaran.||||Penerapan penggunaan Mypertamina untuk membeli pertalite dan solar yang dimulai 1 Juli lalu langsung menuai banyak respon.||||Uji coba awal dilakukan di beberapa kota/kabupaten yang tersebar di 5 Provinsi antara lain Sumatera Barat, Kalimantan Selatan, Sulawesi Utara, Jawa Barat, dan di Yogyakarta. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305856/tak-punya-smartphone-sopir-angkot-bingung-beli-bbm-dengan-aplikasi-mypertamina

title: What to do if hotels and restaurants levy Service Charge on your bills? All you need to know
description: Amid rising consumer complaints, the Central Consumer Protection Authority (CCPA) has barred hotels and restaurants from levying service charge automatically or by default in food bills and allowed customers to file complaints in case of violation. If any consumer finds that a hotel or restaurant is levying service charge in violation of the guidelines, s/he can request the concerned establishment to remove it from the bill amount. Watch this explainer for full information.|#Hotels #ServiceCharge #Restaurants #Guidelines #CentralConsumerProtectionAuthority #Bill #FoodBill

title: Australian Sikh soldiers at Khalistan event, British Army delegation in Pak raise eyebrows in India
description: India is irked by the recent visits of British & Australian Armies' Sikh delegations to controversial events. A twelve-member Sikh delegation of the British Army visited historical & religious sites in Pakistan on June 28 at the invitation of Pakistan Army chief General Qamar Bajwa. In another case, an Australian Army Sikh delegation was spotted at a pro-Khalistan event in New South Wales. However, the Australian Defence forces distanced itself from the visit of its Sikh contingent. Watch this video to know more.|#India #Pakistan #Australia #Army #SikhDelegation #Khalistan #Bajwa #BritishArmy #AustralianArmy

title: Lifeguard Bit By Shark While Mimicking Distressed Swimmer During Training Exercise
description: Beaches along Nassau County re-opened, but with an urgent message of caution after 33-year-old lifeguard, Zack Gallo was attacked by a shark. Gallo was mimicking a swimmer in distress as part of a training exercise. Records dating back almost 200 years show shark attacks are rare, with most happening around popular surfing beaches like New Smyrna, Florida, where another shark bite occurred yesterday. title: Police Investigation Finds Potential Weapon Linked To Highland Park Shooting
description: Police in Highland Park had a major break in the investigation discovering a high-powered rifle apparently used in the shooting and left behind when the attacker fled. Investigators checked for fingerprints, and ATF agents launched an immediate trace, based on the unique serial number on the firearm. Police from Chicago and other communities rushed in to help, along with federal agents, who joined hundreds of officers in an intensive search. title: Ina Garten's Roast Duck Breast with Cherries and Port | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network
description: Ina reveals the secret for making this tough meat incredibly tender with her year-round take on an elegant duck dinner!|Subscribe to #discoveryplus to stream more of #BarefootContessa: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgd|Get the recipe â–¶ https://foodtv.com/3yuAvOW|Subscribe to Food Network â–¶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|Ina throws open the doors of her Hamptons home for delicious food, dazzling entertaining ideas and good fun on Barefoot Contessa.|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Roast Duck Breast With Dried Cherries and Port|RECIPE COURTESY OF INA GARTEN|Level: Easy|Total: 7 hr 10 min (includes marinating time)|Active: 35 min|Yield: 4 servings|Ingredients|2 (1-pound) or 4 (8-ounce) Moulard duck breasts|Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper |1 tablespoon canola oil |2 tablespoons unsalted butter |1/2 cup minced shallots (2 shallots) |1 1/2 tablespoons good sherry wine vinegar |3/4 cup ruby Port wine |1/2 cup good chicken stock, preferably homemade |1/2 cup dried cherries |1/4 cup creme fraiche |1 teaspoon grated orange zest |1/4 cup freshly squeezed orange juice |Directions|Wrap each duck breast in plastic wrap and pound them with a meat mallet until each breast is about 1 inch thick. Place the duck on a plate, sprinkle both sides with a total of 4 teaspoons salt, cover with plastic wrap, and refrigerate for at least 6 hours or overnight.|When ready to cook the duck, preheat the oven to 375 degrees F.|Score the skin of the duck breasts with a sharp knife, making a crosshatch pattern but not cutting down to the meat.|In a large (12-inch) heavy-bottomed, ovenproof skillet, heat the oil over medium heat. Place the duck breasts in the pan, skin side down. Cook uncovered over medium heat for 12 to 15 minutes, discarding the fat from the pan occasionally, until the skin is very browned. Turn the duck with tongs, place the skillet in the oven, and roast for 12 to 18 minutes, until the internal temperature of the duck is 120 degrees F for rare. Remove from the oven, cover the pan tightly with aluminum foil, and allow the duck to rest for 10 minutes.|Meanwhile, make the sauce. Melt the butter over medium-high heat in a medium saucepan. Add the shallots and saute for 2 minutes, until tender. Add the vinegar and cook for one minute. Add the Port, chicken stock, cherries, 1 teaspoon salt, and 1/2 teaspoon pepper, bring to a boil, lower the heat, and simmer for 15 minutes. Stir in the crÃ¨me fraÃ®che, orange zest, and orange juice and keep warm over low heat.|Transfer the duck to a cutting board and slice diagonally, fanning the slices out on 4 dinner plates. Spoon the sauce generously on top, sprinkle with salt, and serve hot with extra sauce on the side.|Subscribe to our channel to fill up on the latest must-eat recipes, brilliant kitchen hacks and content from your favorite Food Network shows.|â–¶ FOOD NETWORK KITCHEN APP: http://foodtv.com/FNKApp|â–¶ WEBSITE: https://www.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FULL EPISODES: https://watch.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/FoodNetwork|#InaGarten #BarefootContessa #FoodNetwork #RoastDuckBreast|Ina Garten's Roast Duck Breast with Cherries and Port | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlbZ14SoLqQ

title: Global National: July 4, 2022 | Police detain person of interest in Illinois parade shooting
description: On this episode of Global National: A gunman opened fire at a Fourth of July parade in Highland Park, Ill., near Chicago, killing six people and injuring dozens more. The celebrations quickly turned into chaos, and now police have taken a 22-year-old person of interest into custody in Americaâ€™s latest mass shooting. Mike Armstrong reports on the incident and what witnesses saw.| |In Canada, the Assembly of First Nations (AFN) is about to begin its annual meeting in Vancouver under a cloud of uncertainty. National Chief RoseAnne Archibald has been suspended over allegations of bullying and harassment, which she claims are a "manufactured distraction" from corruption within the organization. Now, as Neetu Garcha reports, Archibald has been removed from the agenda for opening day.| |Ahead of his trip to Canada this month, Pope Francis has given a rare interview. How he addressed rumours about his health, his future at the Vatican, and his thoughts on some current events - Eric Sorensen explains.| |Plus, Russia is declaring victory after capturing the last remaining part of the Luhansk region in eastern Ukraine. Ukrainian soldiers have now pulled out of the strategic city of Lysychansk, as Russian forces move one step closer to capturing the entire Donbas region. As Redmond Shannon explains, itâ€™s also a major comedown from Russian President Vladimir Putinâ€™s initial goals for the invasion.| |And finally, Egyptâ€™s capital is undergoing a major transformation toward modernization. As a result, Cairoâ€™s historic houseboats will be demolished. So what does that mean for residents? title: Chinese Salt and Pepper [Anything]
description: Salt and pepper dishes! Probably the most internationally famous are the Cantonese sort of these, but they're a style that you can see throughout the country.|0:00 â€“ What is salt and pepper seasoning? |1:57 â€“ Version 1, salt and Sichuan pepper seasoning|2:59 â€“ Version 2, salt and white pepper seasoning|3:35 â€“ How to salt and pepper anything|4:17 â€“ Salt and pepper mushrooms|5:45 â€“ Salt and pepper ribs|7:21 â€“ Community Sponsor, Mutclord Whetstones|8:18 â€“ Other salt and pepper mixes?|MUTCLORD WHETSTONES|Link is here, be sure to click the coupon to get 15% off:|https://www.amazon.com/Diamond-Whetstone-Knife-Wet-stone-Sharpening-Stone/dp/B09TJKKV7C?maas=maas_adg_75A28F967A8BA2217688000891377D1A_afap_abs&ref_=aa_maas&tag=maas&th=1|HOW TO MAKE THE SALT & PEPPER MIX|* Whole Sichuan peppercorns (èŠ±æ¤’) -or- white peppercorns (ç™½èƒ¡æ¤’), ~1/2 tbsp|* Salt, ~1/2 tsp|* MSG (å‘³ç²¾), 1/4 tsp|Over a medium-low flame, toast the peppercorns for about three minutes until fragrant (and if using Sichuan peppercorns, until the peppercorns have a slight oily sheen to them). Transfer to a mortar, pound into a powder. Pass the powder through a fine mesh sieve to catch the bits that aren't broken down enough - you should have about 1 tsp of powder in the end.|Toast the salt and also pound that into a powder. If your MSG is the sort that's larger crystals, also pound that into a powder as well.|The final ratio of the mix will be 1 tsp toasted and pounded peppercorns, 1/2 tsp toasted and pounded salt, and 1/4 tsp MSG.|SALT & PEPPER MUSHROOMS|This dish is originally a Sichuan dish, and goes great with the Sichuan peppercorn version of the salt & pepper mix. |* Oyster mushrooms, 500g|* To marinate: salt, 1/4 tsp; sugar, 1/2 tsp; soy sauce (ç”ŸæŠ½), 1/2 tsp|* Starch coating: cornstarch (ç‰ç±³ç”Ÿç²‰), ~3 tbsp and rice flour (ç²˜ç±³ç²‰), ~3 tbsp (the rice flour can be subbed with additional cornstarch)|* Oil, for deep frying|* Salt & pepper seasoning from above (it should be ~1.75 tsp)|Wash your mushrooms, then blanch for about three minutes. Remove, let them cool down. Once they're cool enough to handle, squeeze out the liquid that's in the mushrooms. Pat dry. Mix with the ingredients from the marinade.|Immediately before frying, mix the mushrooms with the starch. Get a wok of oil up to ~180C (or until bubbles are rapidly forming around a pair of chopsticks), and drop the mushrooms in one by one. Fry until they've released their moisture and feel obviously 'hard' if you pulled a pair of chopsticks through them, ~7 minutes.|Remove the oil from the wok. Wipe with a paper towel. Over a medium-low flame, combine the mushrooms with the salt & pepper seasoning in the wok. |SALT & PEPPER RIBS|This dish is originally a Cantonese dish, and goes great with the white peppercorn version of the salt & pepper mix.|* Pork ribs, cut into ~2 inch sections, 1kg|* For the alkaline soak: sodium carbonate (ç¢±é¢) -or- kansui (æ§æ°´), 1 tsp; enough water to submerge the ribs|* To marinate: salt, 1/2 tbsp; soy sauce (ç”ŸæŠ½), 1/2 tbsp; liaojiu a.k.a. Shaoxing wine (æ–™é…’/ç»é…’), 1/2 tbsp|* Starch coating: cornstarch (ç‰ç±³ç”Ÿç²‰), ~3 tbsp and rice flour (ç²˜ç±³ç²‰), ~3 tbsp (the rice flour can be subbed with additional cornstarch)|* Oil, for deep frying|* Garlic, 1 clove, minced|* Salt & pepper seasoning from above (it should be ~1.75 tsp)|* Optional: mild chilis -or- bell pepper, mix of green and red (for looks)|Soak the ribs with the alkaline solution for one hour. Then drain, and leave the ribs running under a trickle of running water for 5-10 minutes, jostling every so often.|Remove the ribs, and move to a towel/rag. An old t-shirt is perfect. Wrap the ribs and *really* make sure you've dried them out. I like to also pat dry with a paper towel for good measure. Transfer to a bowl, marinate the ribs.|Immediately before frying, coat the ribs with the starch. Fry the ribs at 145C for about 5 minutes, or until a chopstick can poke through. Remove, crank the temperature to ~195C, give a second fry for ~30 seconds.|Remove the oil, wipe down the wok. Medium low flame, fry the garlic until fragrant. Add the ribs, mix. Add the seasoning, mix. Add the optional chilis, mix.|SICHUAN PEPPERCORN SOURCING|In this video we used quality Sichuan peppercorns - often the ones exported to the west can be seed-y, stem-y, and generally a little sad. For good Sichuan peppercorns online, check out Mala Market, Fly By Jing, or 50 Hertz:|https://themalamarket.com/collections/sichuan-spices-dry-goods/products/red-sichuan-pepper-hua-jiao|https://flybyjing.com/shop/tribute-pepper/|https://50hertzfoods.com/products/dried-red-sichuan-pepper|______________|And check out our Patreon if you'd like to support the project!|http://www.patreon.com/ChineseCookingDemystified|Outro Music: à¸„à¸´à¸”à¸–à¸¶à¸‡à¸„à¸¸à¸“à¸ˆà¸±à¸‡ by à¸˜à¸²à¸™à¸´à¸™à¸—à¸£à¹Œ à¸­à¸´à¸™à¸—à¸£à¹€à¸—à¸|Found via My Analog Journal (great channel): https://youtu.be/GHaL5H-VYRg

title: State Of Emergency Declared In Akron, Ohio Following Fatal Police Shooting
description: A state of emergency is now declared in Akron, Ohio after protesters took to the streets over a fatal police shooting. The city released body camera footage of the moment eight officers unleashed a barrage of bullets on one 25-year-old man who was unarmed. Many are protesting and demanding justice for Jayland Walker, the victim. title: How Kevin Became Host  | Ask This Old House
description: In this video, Ask This Old House host Kevin O'Connor explains how he landed one of the most important jobs on the staffâ€”without even trying.|SUBSCRIBE to This Old House: http://bit.ly/SubscribeThisOldHouse.|Kevin O'Connor explains how he became the host of ASK and This Old House. With a bright future in finance, Kevin and his wife sent in a letter to This Old House about their home at the same time Ask This Old House was starting. A few weeks after the crew performed a house call at Kevin's home, he received the job offer from the production crew, and the rest is history.|Host Kevin O'Connor never dreamed of hosting Ask This Old House, but a string of good luck seemed to drop the job into his lap.|Kevin was always a fan of This Old House and enjoyed working with his hands. When he and his wife bought their first home, they purposely looked for a fixer-upper. After handling some of the projects themselves, the O'Connors sent a letter to the This Old House team.|Unknown to him, a new show was already in the works: Ask This Old House. After receiving his letter, the crew arrived at Kevin's house for a house call. The crew helped Kevin handle some projects around his home, and his personality sparked an interest. About a month later, Kevin received a phone call from the production team asking if he would be interested in hosting the show, and he knew he couldn't turn it down.|While he was excited to take the job, Kevin didn't think it would last long. As he explained his leaving to his then-boss in the finance industry, Kevin asked him to keep a spot open, as he thought he'd be back in the finance world in around 12 months. That was almost 20 years ago.|Kevin got his start by working with the crew of experts and tradespeople. Plumbing and heating expert Richard Trethewey had Kevin dig ditches. General contractor Tom Silva put Kevin to work cutting wood. He built his skillset with on-the-job training, but his excitement for new projects and to learn never needed bolstering.|Kevin's favorite part of his job is when he gets to work side-by-side with the crew. He finds satisfaction in working with his hands and appreciates the opportunity to shift from the host to the crew. He tries to hand his love and satisfaction down to his kids with projects around their home, hoping that it might stick with them. His other hope? That his kids don't work in television.|Looking for more step by step guidance on how to complete projects around the house? Covering topics from landscaping to electrical to HVAC and plumbing to painting and more. Ask This Old House features the experts from This Old House, including general contractor Tom Silva, plumbing and heating expert Richard Trethewey, landscape contractor Jenn Nawada, master carpenter Norm Abram, and host Kevin Oâ€™Connor. title: Charlo vs Montiel FULL FIGHT: June 19, 2021 | PBC on Showtime
description: (June 19, 2021) Jermall Charlo retained his WBC World Middleweight title and improves to 32-0 (22 KOs) following a dominant unanimous decision victory over rugged Juan Macias Montiel.|Undefeated WBC Middleweight World Champion Jermall Charlo successfully defended his title with a unanimous decision shutout victory over courageous challenger Juan Montiel in an action-packed night of boxing Saturday night live on SHOWTIME from Toyota Center in Houston, Texas in a Premier Boxing Champions event.|Charlo and Montiel both played an equal part in the electrifying main event that capped off a special Juneteenth Day boxing celebration. Charlo threw a career-high 769 punches, yet the gritty, relentless Montiel refused to go down. Instead, Montiel continued to walk forward despite taking incredible punishment, earning Charloâ€™s respect in the process for his guts and character.|Charlo landed more than twice the amount of punches as Montiel (258-127), including a career-high 201 power punches. Montiel miraculously survived a grueling sixth round, despite being on the receiving end of 36 punches landed, a majority of them thrown with malice behind them.  |In the eighth round, Charlo suffered the first cut of his career as Montiel continued to return punches and opened up a gash over Charloâ€™s right eye. Still, Montiel was far out-classed in terms of boxing ability and athleticism. Despite being unable to close the show in front of the raucous hometown crowd, Charlo displayed his well-rounded game, using a variety of punches to deliver shot after shot on Montiel.|#JermallCharlo #CharloMontiel #FullFight|Visit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.||||SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: ||||https://pbcham.ps/FightAlerts||||FOLLOW US:||||https://twitter.com/premierboxing||https://instagram.com/premierboxing||https://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

title: What we know about gunman after 6 killed, 24 injured in Chicago Fourth of July parade shooting
description: An American celebration was interrupted by gunfire, death, and fear. Local 4 is tracking the search for a gunman after a mass shooting at a Fourth of July parade in Illinois.   That terror has stunned the community of Highland Park, a northern suburb of Chicago.  People have been told to shelter in place as the gunman remains on the loose. That's one frightening question mark hanging over this crime, where is the gunman.

title: What we know about the Highland Park mass shooting
description: A mass shooting at a Fourth of July parade in a Chicago suburb Monday left at least six people dead and two dozen injured. title: Kevin Durant isn't looking for a reunion with GS, talks Jeanie Buss' tweet, Kyrie | NBA | THE HERD
description: Ric Bucher joins Colin Cowherd on this Holiday Monday to talk the latest in NBA news, starting off with the trade rumors surrounding Kevin Durant. Ric talks to Colin about the likelihood of KD landing with his former team, the Golden State Warriors, and if he even thinks KD is up for that. Plus, the two discuss why Durant isn't a player that easily fits into a team's culture, and whether that may prove to be an issue for his future organization. title: Where Kevin Durant suits up next season, Kyrie Irving-Russell Westbrook trade talks | NBA | THE HERD
description: Last week, Kevin Durant requested a trade from the Brooklyn Nets. The Miami Heat and Phoenix Suns are at the top of his wish list, but this brings up the issue of whether teams have the stock to trade for him. The Golden State Warriors are reportedly interested in a reunion, but would KD return to the champs? Colin Cowherd shares where he believes the best landing spot is for KD. The Los Angeles Lakers and Brooklyn Nets are reportedly discussing a Kyrie Irving-Russell Westbrook trade. LeBron James is also reportedly pushing for it. With the LeBron-Lakers era potentially ending soon, it is crucial for the team to push towards a trade. title: Kejanggalan yang Disorot Tempo dalam Pengelolaan ACT
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV -  Presiden ACT, Ibnu Khajar memberi tanggapan soal dugaan penyelewangan yang diungkap Tempo.||||Ibnu Khajar menyatakan kondisi keuangan ACT saat ini dalam keadaan baik.||||Terkait dengan besaran gaji pimpinan ACT yang sempat ditulis Tempo dengan nilai fantastis, Presiden ACT justru mengklaim telah terjadi pengurangan gaji.||||Jika dugaan tersebut benar, lalu berapa besar nilai pemborosan dan penyewengan yang dilakukan?||||Lalu bagaimana pertanggung jawabannya pada donatur dan publik?||||Kami membahasnya bersama dua  narasumber  yaitu Direktur Pemberitaan Tempo Budi Setyarso bersama Wakil Ketua Komisi VIII DPR Ace Hasan Syadzily. ||||----||||Sahabat Kompas TV juga bisa memperoleh informasi terkini melalui website: https://www.kompas.tv ||||Media sosial Kompas TV:||||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/KompasTV ||||Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kompastv ||||Twitter: https://twitter.com/KompasTV |||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305815/kejanggalan-yang-disorot-tempo-dalam-pengelolaan-act

title: Taliban minister asked when Afghan girls can return to school - BBC News
description: The Taliban's health minister has said there are "some concerns" about the separate system of teenage girls' education in Afghanistan.|It is 290 days since the Taliban banned girls from attending secondary schools.|Taliban Public Health Minister Dr Qalandar Ebad said: "The teaching of Islam states that men and women are equal, that is clearâ€¦ but we have some concerns about the syllabus, we have some concerns about the hijab and some concerns about the separate system.â€|It comes as human rights groups have criticised an all-male gathering of more than 4,500 of Taliban leaders, clerics and leaders for not addressing concerns about the rights of women and girls.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Afghanistan #BBCNews

title: DUNCAN FERGUSON'S FAREWELL | Everton Giant leaves to pursue managerial ambition
description: Everton can confirm that Duncan Ferguson has left his role as First-Team Assistant Manager to pursue his managerial ambition.|The Club legend, inducted as an Everton Giant in 2011 after two memorable stints as a player at Goodison Park -  in which he captained the side under three different managers - returned to the Blues to coach in the Academy that same year and in 2014, after working as Under-18s Assistant Manager and gaining his UEFA Pro coaching licence, was promoted to a position with the First Team.|The Scot underlined his iconic status with two spells as caretaker manager. The first of those in December 2019 saw Ferguson oversee a victory over Chelsea at a rocking Goodison and go unbeaten in further matches against Manchester United and Arsenal.|Subscribe to Everton Football Club's official YouTube Channel: http://bit.ly/2wtCEbB|Follow us on Facebook: http://facebook.com/everton|Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/everton|Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/everton|Welcome to the Official Everton Football Club YouTube channel. We'll offer fans real insight into life at Goodison Park, Finch Farm and on the road with the Blues.

title: UHOH! FOUND A WEAKNESS - First Aston Martin DBS Nurburgring Laps
description: I couldn't be in Germany with my Aston Martin DBS and not take it for a first lap at the NÃ¼rburgring Nordschleife! After a blast up the derestricted Autobahn to let the V12 purr, let's see how it handles the famous Green Hell as it follows the rite of passage for all Shmeemobiles.|Having made a spontaneous trip to the continent and a long journey out, it's almost immediately time to turn back around for the return journey, this time taking in some stretches of the famously open speed-limited German motorways. With busy roads all over due to the holiday season, there are only a few moments to let the V12 come to life until arrival in the Eifel Mountains.|Nearly all members of my garage have at some point been for a lap at the NÃ¼rburgring, and of course the Aston Martin DBS has to be no exception. While it is very much a grand touring in character, and perhaps rather soft for the bumpy undulations of this particular loop, it's still very much a fun time putting down the power and enjoying a Touristenfahrten session.|Afterwards it's straight back on the road for the onward journey back to London; a total day drive of over 1,000km (600+ miles) and about 15 hours on the road.|Awesome thumbnail pic from GT Carshots, be sure to check out pics of your laps and GP sessions at RaceTracker.de as well!|https://www.racetracker.de|https://www.instagram.com/gt.carshots/|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:03 Heading to the NÃ¼rburgring|02:31 Autobahn Leg|07:14 Arriving in NÃ¼rburg|09:06 Nordschleife Lap|19:12 Onwards to the UK|20:33 Arrival at the Eurotunnel|22:55 Welcome to the UK|23:10 We've Arrived|24:24 Wrap Up|#AstonMartin #Nurburgring #RoadTrip|||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: Serangan Semakin Intens Pasca-Kunjungan Jokowi, Pengamat: Tak Mudah Meminta Rusia Hentikan Perang
description: KOMPAS.TV - Perang antara Rusia dan Ukraina semakin memanas sejak pecah sejak 24 Februari 2022.||||PBB berupaya mendamaikan, namun perang belum reda.||||Presiden Joko Widodo pun berinisiatif menemui Presiden Ukraina Volodymyr Zelenskyy dan Presiden Rusia Vladimir Putin untuk membawa pesan perdamaian.||||Presiden Jokowi juga menyampaikan argumen perang yang berkepanjangan akan mengganggu pasokan pupuk dan gandum bagi dunia.||||Baik dari Ukraina maupun Rusia.||||Jokowi menyebut membawa pesan dari Presiden Zelenskyy untuk Presiden Putin.||||Usai bertemu Presiden Vladimir Putin, Presiden Jokowi juga menegaskan telah menyampaikan pesan dari Presiden Zelenskyy.||||Namun, Sekretaris Pers untuk Kantor Presiden Ukraina, Serhii Nikiforov membantah soal titipan pesan Presiden Zelenskyy untuk Presiden Putin.||||Kepada Media Ukrainska Pravda, Serhii Nikiforov mengatakan jika Zelenskyy ingin berbicara kepada Putin dia akan melakukannya di depan umum.||||Indonesia adalah salah satu pengimpor gandum terbesar dari Ukraina dan blokade pada Pelabuhan Ukraina menjadi fokus utama pembicaraan diantara kedua presiden di Kyiv.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305833/serangan-semakin-intens-pasca-kunjungan-jokowi-pengamat-tak-mudah-meminta-rusia-hentikan-perang

title: Parts of India parched, others badly flooded as climate change affects monsoon season | DW News
description: India's monsoon season has been slow to start this year, but now rains have covered the entire country. title: Why Modi govt raised duty on gold to cut imports, why it will cheer smugglers

title: Former SpaceX Rocket Scientist Now Makes High-Tech Pizza
description: Making pizza is not rocket science, but for this actual rocket scientist it is now. Benson Tsai is a former SpaceX employee who is now using his skills to launch a new venture: Stellar Pizza, a fully automated, mobile pizza delivery service. When a customer places an order on an app, an algorithm decides when to start making the pizza based on how long it will take to get to the delivery address. Inside Edition Digitalâ€™s Mara Montalbano has more.

title: Stress im Nationalpark - Wenn Touristen zum Problem werden | Die Nordreportage | NDR Doku
description: Die Nationalparks sind voll von Besucherinnen und Besuchern. Schon vor Corona bestand das Problem, das sich aufgrund von Digitalisierung und Pandemie deutlich verstÃ¤rkt hat. Die Rangerinnen und Ranger kÃ¶nnen nicht mehr das tun, wozu sie ausgebildet wurden: die Natur zu schÃ¼tzen und Besucherinnen und Besucher aufzuklÃ¤ren. Stattdessen mÃ¼ssen sie quasi rund um die Uhr die Nationalparks vor dem Massenansturm der Touristen schÃ¼tzen und Deeskalation betreiben.|Doch nicht nur die gestiegene Anzahl an Touristen und moderne Tracking-Wander- und -Fahrrad-Apps, die Menschen querfeldein durch die Naturparks lenken, bringen Stress und neue Herausforderungen mit sich, auch die Klientel hat sich verÃ¤ndert, der Ton ist rauer geworden: AggressivitÃ¤t und Unwissenheit machen es den Parkangestellten immer schwerer, den Leuten die Regeln fÃ¼r die Naturschutzgebiete nahezubringen.|Manche von ihnen sprechen vom "Ballermann"-Tourismus, wenn ParkgÃ¤ste sich in den geschÃ¼tzten Kernzonen der DÃ¼nen niederlassen zum Wildcamping, Picknick oder Saufen, wenn Windeln und anderer Abfall im Wald liegen gelassen werden, die Menschen sich querfeldein abseits der Wege bewegen, Hunde nicht angeleint, auf den Kreidefelsen herumgeturnt oder Selfies fÃ¼r Instagram an der Abbruchkante gemacht werden.|Der Film zeigt den Alltag von vier Rangerinnen und Rangern im Nationalpark Jasmund und im Nationalpark Vorpommersche Boddenlandschaft und ihren tÃ¤glichen Kampf gegen den Ansturm der Menschenmassen und deren Fehlverhalten.|Weitere Infos zum Thema: https://www.ndr.de/fernsehen/sendungen/die_nordreportage/Stress-im-Nationalpark,sendung1265552.html|Erstausstrahlung: 4. title: Eye on AMCA fighter project & IAFâ€™s Rafale, French engine makerâ€™s MRO facility in India soon
description: Giving a further boost to the Narendra Modi government's ambitious 'Aatmanirbhar Bharat' campaign, French engine-maker Safran will set up a Maintenance Repair and Overhaul facility for leading-edge aviation propulsion (LEAP) commercial aircraft engines. The MRO facility will be set up by the company as part of its offset commitments. As per reports, Safran will invest $150 million in setting up the facility. Sources told HT that the MRO facility, said to be based either in Hyderabad or Bengaluru, will apparently be announced tomorrow when Safran CEO Olivier Andres meets Indian Civil Aviation Minister Jyotiraditya Scindia. It also aims to further its proposal to co-develop with DRDO's Gas Turbine Research Establishment a 110kn thrust engine for the fifth-generation advanced medium combat aircraft twin-engine (AMCA) fighter project. title: How Stranger Things' Joseph Quinn Learned To Play Metallica's 'Master Of Puppets' | News
description: The finale of 'Stranger Things' season 4 featured a performance of Metallica's classic 'Master Of Puppets'. Eddie Munson actor Joseph Quinn has revealed in a new interview how he learned to play the track, which featured additional guitar work from Rob Trujillo's son Tye. The song has shot up the global Spotify chart as a result of being featured in the finale - could it see the same level of success as Kate Bush's 'Running Up That Hill'? Plus, Jamie Campbell Bower talks the importance of music to the Netflix show and we look back into the archive as BABYMETAL, Trivium and Biffy Clyro tell us what Metallica mean to them.|Host: James Wilson-Taylor|#Metallica #StrangerThings #MasterOfPuppets|Subscribe to Rock Sound's YouTube channel: http://bit.ly/XYvFPb||||Get the best interviews, music videos and more from the wide world of alternative music.||See what else we do: http://www.rocksound.tv||||Rock Sound Magazine is available worldwide: ||Download the digital edition: http://smarturl.it/rsapp ||Order a copy direct to your door: http://shop.rocksound.tv

This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. title: After Lysychansk, Russia Eyes Sloviansk l Why This Battle Can Help Putin Achieve Ukraine War Goal
description: After Russia captured the eastern Ukrainian city of Lysychansk, its troops are turning their attention to the city of Sloviansk. Residents of Sloviansk, a city of just over 100,000 people before the invasion, are now being urged to evacuate. As per reports, Russian troops were attempting to push Ukrainian forces back to a new defensive line between Siversk, Soledar and Bakhmut. On July 3, Ukrainian authorities said six people were killed in the Russian shelling of Sloviansk and another 19 people were wounded.|#RussiaUkraineWar #Sloviansk #BattleForDonbas|0:00 - INTRODUCTION|1:30 - WILL HISTORY REPEAT ITSELF IN SLOVIANSK?|2:12 -IMPORTANCE OF SLOVIANSK |CRUX is your daily video news guide to the big events that are shaping our world. Erneut mÃ¼ssen mÃ¤chtige Bosse mit neuen Ideen besiegt, RÃ¤tsel gelÃ¶st und Charakteren geholfen werden. FrÃ¤ulein Kelch kann hierbei sogar selbst aktiv werden und ihre einzigartigen FÃ¤higkeiten zusammen mit neuen Waffen und Amuletten im Kampf nutzen. Sie beherscht eine Ausweichrolle am Boden, einen Doppelsprung und kann extrem schnell parieren und dabei nach vorne huschen. Sie kann sowohl fÃ¼r den DLC als auch fÃ¼r das Hauptspiel hergenommen werden, mit wem man spielt bleibt den Gamern Ã¼berlassen.|Cuphead "Donâ€™t Deal With the Devil" ist ein Shoot-â€™em-up mit Jump'n'Run Elementen im Cartoon-Stil der frÃ¼hen 1930er Jahre, welches stilistisch an die Werke von Walt Disney und Max Fleischer sowie ihrem verwendeten Surrealismus angelehnt ist und vom kanadischen Indie-Entwickler StudioMDHR am 29.09.2017 fÃ¼r PC und Xbox One verÃ¶ffentlicht wurde. Mittlerweile ist das Spiel allerdings fÃ¼r alle gÃ¤ngigen Plattformen erhÃ¤ltlich. |Bekannt geworden ist Cuphead neben seinem besonderen Artstil, bei dem alle Inhalte Ã¼brigens von Hand gezeichnet wurden, durch den relativ hohen Schwierigkeitsgrad. Im Spiel mÃ¼ssen Tassilo & Pottkopp, die sich beim Versuch durch GlÃ¼cksspiel ans schnelle Geld zu kommen mit dem Teufel angelegt haben, ihre Seelen retten, indem sie dem Teufel andere bringen. Allesamt starke Gegner, welche dem Teufel Geld schulden. Das Game besteht somit groÃŸteils aus in mehrere Phasen unterteilten BosskÃ¤mpfen, die mit verschiedenen Schusswaffen, Spezialangriffen und taktischen Items wie einer "Ausweich-Rauchbombe" angegangen werden kÃ¶nnen. Viele KÃ¤mpfe finden auf dem Erdboden statt, es gibt aber auch Luftschlachten, welche mit einem Flugzeug bestritten werden. Der Spieler kann hierbei kontinuierlich feuern, hÃ¤lt selbst aber nur 3 gegnerische Treffer aus. Mit jedem Treffer den der Spieler landet lÃ¤dt sich die Spezialangriffsleiste, welche durch maximal 5 Spielkarten visualisiert wird, auf. Eine weitere MÃ¶glichkeit diese aufzuladen, ist das Parieren. Alle rosanen Angriffe und Elemente im Spiel kÃ¶nnen pariert werden! Man kann eine Karte fÃ¼r einen starken Angriff nutzen oder alle 5 fÃ¼r einen "Super"-Move. Jede Waffe hat unterschiedliche normale und starke Angriffe. Die Ultis mÃ¼ssen auf der Oberwelt in Mausoleen freigeschaltet werden. Die Waffen abseits der Standardwaffe, welche von Anfang an verfÃ¼gbar ist, kann man sich mit begrenzten GoldmÃ¼nzen in einem Item-Laden, den es in jeder der drei Hauptwelten gibt, kaufen. Diese MÃ¼nzen findet man zum Teil versteckt in den Oberwelten, bekommt sie durch Sidequests, allen voran aber in den sogenannten "Run'n'Gun"-Leveln, welche ein forderndes Jump'n'Run Level mit dem typischen Shoot-â€™em-up Gameplay darstellen.|Cuphead gewann zahlreiche Preise, erntete Topwertungen (88%) und verkaufte sich Ã¼ber fÃ¼nf Millionen Mal.|Das Spiel verfÃ¼gt Ã¼ber einen lokalen Koop-Modus. Mother Gay Longworth discovered her 13-year-old daughter Roxy had been coerced into sending explicit images to a boy four years her senior when she received a phonecall from her school. title: Dihadang Santri, Tersangka Pencabulan di Jombang Gagal Ditangkap Polisi
description: KOMPAS.TV - Polda Jawa Timur gagal menjemput paksa tersangka pencabulan di Jombang, Jawa Timur. Polisi dihadang para santri saat hendak memasuki pesantren.||||Upaya jemput paksa yang dilakukan polisi terhadap tersangka kasus pencabulan santri di Jombang, Jawa Timur kembali mendapat penghadangan.||||Baca Juga Update Kasus Dugaan Pencabulan di Ponpes Riyadhul Jannah Depok, 11 Santriwati Jadi Korban di https://www.kompas.tv/article/304723/update-kasus-dugaan-pencabulan-di-ponpes-riyadhul-jannah-depok-11-santriwati-jadi-korban||||Sudah dua tahun berjalan, kasus pelecehan seksual dan pencabulan yang dilakukan oleh anak pengasuh pesantren di Jombang ini tak kunjung bisa ditangani polisi.||||Beberapa kali melakukan upaya penangkapan, tersangka selalu dilindungi oleh ratusan santri.||||Polisi pun harus menurunkan ratusan personil dari brimob, polda, hingga kodim.||||Kasus pencabulan terjadi Oktober 2019 lalu, penetapan tersangka dilakukan usai polisi mendapat laporan dari korban seorang santriwati dan penyidikan.||||Namun hingga kini tersangka masih bebas berkeliaran tanpa adanya penahanan.||||Meski telah ditetapkan sebagai DPO polisi masih kesulitan karena mendapat hadangan dari para santri.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305742/dihadang-santri-tersangka-pencabulan-di-jombang-gagal-ditangkap-polisi

title: LeT terrorist Talib Shah's pics with BJP leaders stirs row; J&K party chief smells Pak plot
description: Among the two Lashkar-e-Taiba terrorists captured yesterday by villagers in Jammu and Kashmir's Reasi, was a BJP leader, Talib Hussain Shah. He was the BJP Minority Morcha's social media in-charge in Jammu. He, along with one Faizal Ahmed Dar, were apprehended by villagers in Tuksan, Reasi district. Some pictures emerged on social media purportedly showing Shah with BJP leaders. One of the pictures shows J&K BJP president Ravinder Raina presenting him with a bouquet. Another one, posted by J&K Congress, showed Talib Shah sharing a dais with Home Minister Amit Shah. The J&K unit of the BJP, however, denied that Talib Shah was in-charge of the partyâ€™s minority morcha IT cell, saying the allegation was worrying as falsely implicating the BJP had become a new modus-operandi for Pakistan-based terror outfits. title: Rusia Makin Sengit Serang Ukraina Pasca Kunjungan Jokowi? Ini Kata Pengamat!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Pengamat Hubungan Internasional Suzie Sudarman menilai serangan rusia semakin sengit ke Ukraina Pasca-Kunjungan Presiden Jokowi merupakan upaya persuasif dari Rusia.||||Menurutnya, Rusia sebagai negara adidaya tak mudah dipengaruhi untuk segera menghentikan perang.||||Suzie menegaskan keberhasilan misi perdamaian Presiden Jokowi juga bergantung pada respon Rusia.||||Baca Juga Pengamat: Kunjungan Jokowi ke Ukraina dan Rusia Strategi untuk Sukseskan G20 di Indonesia di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305664/pengamat-kunjungan-jokowi-ke-ukraina-dan-rusia-strategi-untuk-sukseskan-g20-di-indonesia||||Menurutnya, Rusia sebagai adidaya tak mudah dipengaruhi utuk segera berdamai dengan Ukraina.||||Oleh karena itu, misi Presiden Jokowi dan peran Indonesia dalam mendamaikan Ukraina dan Rusia dinilai akan berjalan panjang.||||Video Editor: Lintang||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305700/rusia-makin-sengit-serang-ukraina-pasca-kunjungan-jokowi-ini-kata-pengamat

title: Chief Minister Eknath Shinde's Speech In Assembly After Trust Vote Win
description: Eknath Shinde broke down today in an emotional speech in the Maharashtra assembly, his first as Chief Minister after an easy trust vote win. While describing what he alleged were threats to his family over his revolt, Eknath Shinde referred to two of his children who had died and choked up. "They attacked my family...My father is alive, my mother died. I could not give much time to my parents. They would be asleep when I came and would go to work when I slept. I could not give much time to my son Shrikant. My two children died - at the time, Anand Dighe consoled me. I used to think, what is there to live for? I will stay with my family," the Chief Minister said.|About NDTV: NDTV brings you unbiased and comprehensive coverage of news and entertainment programmes in India and abroad. title: Taliban commander flies bride in military chopper in Afghanistan? Video goes viral
description: A Taliban commander allegedly used military helicopter to take newly-wed bride home in Afghanistan. Afghan media reports claim that the commander allegedly flew his newlywed bride from Logar to Khost province, in eastern Afghanistan, using the military helicopter. In a video that went viral on social media, the commander is seen as landing near a house. Taliban have dismissed the video and claims as false and enemy propaganda. Watch the video for more.|#taliban #afghanistan #chopper #taliban #logar #haqqaninetwork #usarmy #viralvideo #kabul #khost

title: POLYMER CLAY VS. RESIN | Cute Mini Crafts And DIY Accessories
description: Hi guys! If you want some cool things that you can't afford, you can make this fancy stuff yourself! Just imagine, a miniature cocktail hanging on your ear - your friends will be amazed! Are you a food person, but don't like sweets? No problem, you make mini hot dog out of polymer clay. Looks so realistic! Are you going to doubt it? So, try real food! Take a bunch of jelly bears to make cool bracelet! If you're into pastel style, you'll definitely adore transparent resin pendant with flowers inside. And, yeah, when you'll finish making your stunning jewelry set, you should have a jewelry holder out of epoxy, too! Last but not least: you can even repair things with clay or resin! Go and try it on some broken wires to protect yourself with style! ||Don't focus only on polymer clay and epoxy, go and watch some videos about using plastic, paper, 3D pen and glue gun, you'll be inspired, we promise! And quick poll: CLAY or RESIN? Which one do you like more? title: Welcome to The Arsenal, Gabriel Jesus!
description: Gabriel Jesus has signed from Manchester City on a long-term contract.|The 25-year-old forward joins us having established himself as one of the leading strikers in the Premier League in recent seasons. He scored 95 goals in 236 appearances in all competitions during his five seasons in Manchester.|Gabriel has won the Premier League title four times, the FA Cup, and the League Cup three times. He is a regular in the Brazil national team, making 56 appearances and scoring 19 times since making his full international debut for his country in September 2016. He was a member of the squad which won the Copa America in 2019. During his international career Gabriel has also notably won a gold medal at the 2016 Rio Olympic Games, and featured at the 2018 FIFA World Cup.|Gabriel developed through the youth setup at Palmeiras, signing a youth contract in 2013, with his prolific goalscoring ensuring he quickly progressed into the first-team squad, making his debut as a 17-year-old in March 2015. During his time with Palmeiras, Gabriel was an integral part of the clubâ€™s Campeonato Brasileiro Serie A winning side in 2016, when he was voted as the leagueâ€™s Bola de Ouro â€“ Player of the Season. |Technical Director Edu said: â€œWe are delighted that we have secured the transfer of Gabriel. Everyone who knows football well, knows the qualities of Gabriel Jesus.|"Gabriel is a player who we have admired for a long time now. He is 25 years old and an established Brazil international who has consistently demonstrated that he is a player at a very high level. We look forward to seeing him join up with his new teammates ahead of the new season. We all welcome Gabriel to Arsenal.â€ |Mikel Arteta added: â€œIâ€™m very excited. The club has done a tremendous job to recruit a player of this stature. I know Gabriel personally very well, and we all know him well from his time in the Premier League and being really successful here.|"This is a position thatâ€™s been on our radar for a long time now and we have managed to get a player that we all wanted, so Iâ€™m really happy.â€|Gabriel will wear the number 9 shirt and will join up with the Gunners squad for pre-season training soon.|#arsenal #gabrieljesus |Subscribe to the Official Arsenal YouTube Channel: https://arsn.al/youtube|Follow us on Facebook: https://arsn.al/facebook|Follow us on Twitter: https://arsn.al/twitter|Follow us on Instagram: https://arsn.al/instagram|Follow us on TikTok: https://arsn.al/tiktok|This is the Official YouTube channel for Arsenal Football Club.|For more match action, highlights and training videos, make sure you become a digital member and sign up to Arsenal Player. It's FREE and is the Home of the Game: https://arsn.al/arsenalplayer|Arsenal Football Club were formed in 1886 and amassed 13 League titles, 14 FA Cups. Some of their greatest players include: Thierry Henry, Dennis Bergkamp, Tony Adams, Ian Wright, Robert Pires, Liam Brady, Patrick Vieira, Cliff Bastin and Charlie George.

title: Tour de France 2022: Which smart trainers do they use?
description: Here's your behind-the-scenes look in the team warm-up area at Tour de France 2022 and which smart trainers each of the teams uses.|When it comes to the massive logistical challenge that is transporting a team and all their cycling gear across 21 stages and four countries for the 2022 Tour de France, one perhaps unexpected bit of gear is their smart trainers. Each time brings a slate of trainers with them, and in some cases, multiple types of trainers â€“ and often enough for all riders, depending on the year/stages.|That was certainly the case this past weekend at the Tour de France when opening stage was an individual time trial, as it often is. That means that each rider typically warms up on a smart trainer ahead of that stage for perhaps 25-40 minutes, before competing the relatively short 13KM stage. This will play out again later in the Tour de France on the 2nd to last stage, where a much longer 40.7km individual time trial is set to happen. There are no team time trials this year (unfortunately, they make for spectacular photos).|As is often the case for many years, Iâ€™ve outlined which trainers and power meters each team uses, as well as lots of interesting little trainer tidbits along the way. For this post, weâ€™ve got the trainers up first. Iâ€™m skipping the bike power meters on todayâ€™s post, because power meters on time trial bikes are very often different than their road bikes they use for the rest of the Tour (which accounts for like 99% of the milage). Same goes for bike computers and such. More on that later.|Elite Direto XR:|- B&B Hotelsâ€“KTM|- Cofidis|- Team DSM (also Elite Qubo spotted)|Elite Justo:|- Groupamaâ€“FDJ|- UAE Team Emirates|Elite Suito:|- AG2R CitroÃ«n Team|- ArkÃ©aâ€“Samsic|- Bahrain Victorious|- IntermarchÃ©â€“Wantyâ€“Gobert MatÃ©riaux|- Israelâ€“Premier Tech|- Movistar Team|Tacx NEO 2T:|- Astana Qazaqstan|- BikeExchangeâ€“Jayco|- Ineos Grenadiers|- Jumboâ€“Visma|- Lottoâ€“Soudal|- Quick-Step Alpha Vinyl|- TotalEnergies-Cyclists|Wahoo KICKR V5/2020:|- Alpecinâ€“Deceuninck|- Boraâ€“Hansgrohe|- EF Educationâ€“EasyPost|- Trekâ€“Segafredo (also Wahoo ROLLR spotted)|#TourdeFrance #LeTour #TourDeFrance2022 #Cycling

title: The Quad is going beyond military exercises â€” and China is watching
description: The Quad, or the Quadrilateral Security Dialogue, comprises four big, democratic economies: the United States, Japan, India and Australia.|Over the years, the Quad has been incorrectly called an â€œAsian NATO,â€ especially when it comes to security concerns around another big power in the region â€” China. |The Quad countries have cooperated in areas ranging from health and infrastructure development to military exercises â€”most notably the Exercise Malabar naval war games, which have developed into a permanent feature of the Quad.  |â€œBecause it has no specific mandate, they can make economic or even global warming issues part of the mandate of the Quad,â€ said Ted Kemp, CNBC International digital managing editor, and author of a game-theory driven project on the future of the Quad. |That includes being an effective counterbalance to Chinaâ€™s dominance in the Indo-Pacific region.  |â€œWhat the Quad countries individually and collectively have been concerned about is about Chinaâ€™s behavior,â€ Tanvi Madan, director of The India Project at the Brookings Institution, told CNBC. â€œThe idea is to provide choice, stability, and to bring resources to the region that otherwise might not have been available.â€ |Watch the video above to learn more about the Quadâ€™s influence in the Indo-Pacific region.|#CNBC #Quad #ShinzoAbe|-----|Subscribe: http://cnb.cx/2wuoARM|CNBC International TV: https://cnb.cx/2NGytpz|Facebook:|https://www.facebook.com/cnbcinternational|Instagram:|https://www.instagram.com/cnbcinternational/|Twitter:|https://twitter.com/CNBCi

title: Indiaâ€™s Cruelest Jail, â€˜Kala Pani, Cellular Jail Port Blairâ€™ | Curly Tales
description: Kamiya Jani recently visited the Cellular Jail, also known as Kala Pani at Port Blair, Andaman Islands. Now a national memorial, this prison is probably the cruelest in the world. Although it had extremely low walls - which meant that a prisoner could easily scale them, they would ultimately plunge to his death as the prison was surrounded by the ocean on all sides. The prison was also constructed in a way that the front portion of each wing was to face the back side of the other wing so that no prisoner could see one another during confinement. Sounds terrible doesnâ€™t it?| |Today, the horrifying prison is a memorial dedicated to the Indian freedom fighters and political activists struggling for India's independence. There is a beautiful Light & Sound show that takes place in the evenings which captures the entire history of Kala Pani.  This is a must-visit show for every tourist. It is held thrice a day both in English and Hindi.|#curlytales #kamiyajani #kalapani #cellularjail #portblair #andaman #jail #ilovemyindia #incredibleindia |Subscribe to Curly Tales on YT â–º http://bit.ly/CurlyTales|Other Social Accounts:|Follow us on Facebook â–ºhttp://bit.ly/2PEaDGT|Follow us on Instagram â–º http://bit.ly/2NQcckE|For more such stories â–º http://bit.ly/2MM7yrk

title: "Friend Died After Saving Me": Manipur Landslide Survivor Recounts Horror
description: Romen Phukan, 35, still can't believe he is alive. Haunted by the screams for help after the landslide hit their camp in Manipur last week, he recounts how the horror unfolded - and that he saw his friend die in front of him moments after he saved his life. Mr Phukan was among the 80-odd men who were at the site of the incident on Wednesday night, when a catastrophic landslide washed away their camps in Tupul in Noney district, burying those at the site under boulders and mud. title: Indigo crew plays mass truant for walk-in interviews at rival airline; Flight delays hit carrier
description: More than 55% of Indigo airline's operations were affected on Saturday after a large number of its staff did not report on duty. According to a PTI report, a significant number of staff who called in sick went for the Air India recruitment drive on the same day. This resulted in massive delays and the cancellation of Indigo flights. Both Indigo & Air India are yet to respond and issue an official statement on the matter. The Director-General of Civil Aviation has sought a clarification from Indigo. Watch this video to know more.|#IndiGo #AirIndia #CabinCrew #Staff #Shortage #DGCA #DirectorGeneralOfCivilAviation #RecruitmentDrive

title: Gunman opens fire at Copenhagen mall, terrified shoppers flee; Police probe terror angle
description: Three people were killed and several others injured after a gunman opened fire at one of Denmark's biggest malls, Fields shopping mall. The attacker has been identified as a 22-year-old 'ethnic Dane' and is under custody. The motive behind the attack is not clear, police have begun probing the terror angle. British singer Harry Styles was due to perform later in the evening, at 8 pm at a concert venue less than a mile from the mall. Danish PM Mette Frederiksen condemn the attack and called it 'cruel'. Watch this video to know more.|#Denmark #Copenhagen #ShoppingMall #Shooting #FieldShoppingMall #MetteFrederiksen

title: Kata Ukraina dan Rusia Soal Zelenskyy Titip Pesan Via Jokowi ke Putin
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden Jokowi menyatakan dirinya telah menyampaikan pesan dari Presiden Ukraina Volodymyr Zelenskyy yang dititipkan untuk Presiden Rusia Vladimir Putin pada 30 Juni 2022.||||Namun, pihak kepresidenan Ukraina melalui Juru Bicara Kantor Kepresidenan Ukraina Serhii Nikiforov membantah jika Zelenskyy menitipkan pesan pada Jokowi untuk Putin.||||Menurutnya, Zelenskyy akan menyampaikan sendiri ke publik tanpa perantara.||||Baca Juga Presiden Jokowi Rencanakan Berkurban Sapi di Maluku Utara! Peternak Pastikan Tak Ada PMK di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305581/presiden-jokowi-rencanakan-berkurban-sapi-di-maluku-utara-peternak-pastikan-tak-ada-pmk||||Lalu bagaimana dengan pihak Kremlin terkait dengan hal ini?||||Dari Kantor Berita Rusia, TASS, Juru Bicara Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov mengkonfirmasi adanya pesan dari Zelenskyy yang disampaikan oleh Presiden Jokowi, kepada Presiden Rusia Vladimir Putin.||||Jubir Kremlin menegaskan pesan via Presiden Jokowi tersebut tidak tertulis.||||Video Editor: Lintang||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305614/kata-ukraina-dan-rusia-soal-zelenskyy-titip-pesan-via-jokowi-ke-putin

title: India to Sri Lankaâ€™s â€˜fuel rescueâ€™ again; Will send three ships of petrol & diesel till August
description: India has come to the rescue of Sri Lanka yet again. India will send two ships each of diesel and petrol to the neighbouring island nation facing an acute shortage of fuel. One ship is expected in Sri Lanka between July 13 and 15 and another between July 29 and 31. The last one will reach the island nation between August 10 and 15. Sri Lanka has received more than 400,000 tonne of fuel from India over the past three months. On the other hand, the island nation has even kept schools shut for a week since it doesn't even have enough fuel for students and teachers to reach schools. Watch this video for more information.|#srilanka #fuelcrisis #srilanka #modigovernment #ranilwickremesinghe #petrol #diesel #narendramodi #lanka #economiccrisis #schools

title: Akshay Kumar Is Injured While Performing A Stunt | Waqt | Movie Scene | Vipul Amrutlal Shah
description: After getting humiliated by Ishwar, Adi takes up a job as a stunt double in a Hindi film production. #waqt |Waqt is the story of a father and a son between whom there is a special bond. Unlike many other father son relationships, these two are more like friends; the father being Ishwar Sharawat and his son Aditya .Ishwar is the owner of a toy manufacturing company and is extremely generous and big hearted making sure to spread as much as joy to kids as he can, and that is why he makes sure that during the festive season of Diwali he distributes toys to the orphans. On the surface Ishwar's life seems like something every man would crave for; a great and profitable business, a loving son and a caring and dutiful wife Sumitra or so it seems. Aditya is in love with Mitali and vice-versa who is the daughter of Nathu. However after the initial problems that occur, the two of them finally end up getting married. Ishwar hopes that marriage will make Aditya a more responsible man but he is disappointed. His efforts to turn Aditya into a more responsible individual turn futile. One thing leads to another and Ishwar doesn't have an option but to throw Aditya out of the house. Aditya is shocked that the same doting father is now behaving in this fashion towards him and his now pregnant wife. After the initial problems, Aditya takes it upon himself to take care of his wife and his unborn kid. Aditya starts working as freelance stuntman and at the same time prepares for a star search contest. Aditya starts turning into an independent man but the rift in the relationship between him and his father grows. description: Sunday - 10:52 p.m.||||3News Reporter Neil Fischer provided video from the scene of protests in downtown Akron of what appears to be tear gas being used against protestors. Police in full riot gear can be seen deploying the tear gas. Some city trucks being used to block access to certain roads in the city have had their windows smashed.||||Sunday - 7:52 p.m.||||Sen. Sherrod Brown (D-OH) has issued a statement following the fatal shooting of Jayland Walker:||||â€œThe death of Jayland Walker is a tragedy. The Walker family and the entire Akron community deserve a thorough and transparent investigation of why we are mourning yet another young, Black life cut short. description: El Retiro park is a fun place in Madrid, Spain for chess players. On 2nd of July, on the final rest day of the Candidates tournament, some stars visited the chess park. title: Niat Beralan-jalan bersama Teman ke Air Terjun Tirtosari Jatim, Wisatawan Asal Subang Tertimpa Batu!
description: MAGETAN, KOMPAS.TV - Seorang wisatawan meninggal dunia,  diduga tertimpa longsoran batu di lokasi wisata Air Terjun Tirtosari, Magetan, Jawa Timur.||||Wisatawan  asal Subang, Jawa Barat, meninggal dunia, setelah tertimpa longsoran batu.||||Korban meninggal saat perjalanan ke Rumah Sakit Sayidiman Magetan karena menderita luka di bagian kepala .||||Sementara, dua rekannya menjalani perawatan intensif di IGD Puskesmas Plaosan karena mengalami luka di kepala.||||Peristiwa  bermula saat korban bersama lima rekannya, berkunjung ke Air Terjun Tirtosari.||||Tiba-tiba, batu berukuran besar dari atas, longsor, dan menimpa ke tiga korban.||||_____                                ||||Jangan lewatkan live streaming Kompas TV 24 jam nonstop di https://www.kompas.tv/live.||||Agar tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia. title: SC Nupur lashing: Justice Pardiwala slams 'agenda-driven personalised attacks' after online outrage
description: Social and digital media need to be mandatorily regulated in India to preserve the rule of law under the Constitution, said Supreme Court Judge Justice Jamshed Burjor Pardiwala who has been in the news after a top court bench dismissed former BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma's petition seeking to club all FIRs registered against her for her remarks on Prophet Mohammed. Harsh observations of the top court's vacation bench that sought an apology from Sharma, stating her â€œloose tongue has set the entire country on fireâ€, have received severe backlash from certain corners and faced attacks by the faction that supported the former BJP spokesperson. title: Zhou Guanyu's terrifying British GP crash and how F1 escaped something worse
description: Formula 1 narrowly avoided disaster on more than one occasion in the opening moments of the British Grand Prix. |Not only did Alfa Romeo driver Zhou Guanyu escape unhurt from a terrifying first corner crash, but the resulting red flag saved us from potentially witnessing a tragedy, as it meant protestors that had invaded the track after the start were not encountered by the cars at racing speed. |After those two situations fortunately played out without anyone being harmed, the small matter of a sporting contest took place, and that was filled with plenty of drama as well, particularly for the championship protagonists.|#F1 #BritishGP #Silverstone|READ MORE HERE|https://the-race.com/formula-1/russell-f1-has-to-learn-from-horrible-position-of-zhous-alfa/ |Subscribe: http://the-race.com/youtube_subscribe|Website: http://the-race.com/|Twitter: @wearetherace|Instagram: @wearetherace|Facebook: http://facebook.com/wearetherace|Podcasts: http://the-race.com/podcasts|Thanks for watching - please like, share and comment, please also hit subscribe to show your support so we'll keep doing what we're doing.|https://www.the-race.com|http://www.twitter.com/wearetherace

title: Global National: July 3, 2022 | Russia claims victory over Ukrainian forces in Lysychansk
description: On this episode of Global National: Russia is claiming victory in Ukraine's eastern Luhansk region after capturing the final holdout of Lysychansk, a city that is key to control of the Donbas. As David Akin reports, Russia's advances would now shift the battlefield focus to neighbouring Donetsk, where Ukraine still holds substantial territory.|In Canada, a 13-year-old girl from Edmonton who went missing more than a week ago is back with her family, following an exhaustive international search. The girl disappeared after leaving her home for school, and was only found on Saturday. A 41-year-old Oregon man is now in custody and facing charges of child luring in connection with her disappearance. Morgan Black with the latest.|Plus, this busy holiday weekend is notorious for creating travel headaches, as millions hit the roads and skies to celebrate with friends and family. But a computer scheduling glitch at American Airlines and a nationwide pilot shortage has led to an unusually high number of flight cancellations as drivers deal with record high gas prices. Jennifer Johnson reports.|At the G7 Summit this week, Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau and his fellow leaders announced new details of a $773 billion plan to invest in sustainable infrastructure projects across the developing world. Itâ€™s being seen as the west playing catch-up to Chinaâ€™s decade-old Belt and Road Initiative. Redmond Shannon takes a look at what it will involve and the reasons behind it.|Back home, the ongoing labour shortage in Canada is forcing employers to adapt. Across a wide range of industries, those hiring are becoming less rigid in their expectations of applicants. As Ross Lord explains, the shift is needed so companies can secure enough staff to get the job done.|Finally, as top show horse jumpers from around the world gathered for this yearâ€™s Spruce Meadows â€œPan Americanâ€ Tournament, an Ontario jumping horse gets big support from his little buddy. Named Mimosa, the mini horse helps keep Tito calm before competing as a constant travel companion. Gil Tucker reports.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #GlobalNational
