title: Setelah Jokowi, Giliran PM Australia Anthony Albanese ke Ukraina
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Perdana Menteri Australia Anthony Albanese mengunjungi Irpin pada hari Minggu (3/7/2022). ||||Irpin merupakan salah satu kota yang dilanda perang di wilayah Kyiv Ukraina.||||Albanese mengatakan situasi Irpin hancur akibat penembakan dan menyebutnya sebagai imbas dari kejahatan perang.||||Di depan Albanese, Presiden Ukraina Volodymyr Zelenskyy mengatakan pasukan Kyiv masih memerangi tentara Rusia di pinggiran Lysychansk.||||Baca Juga Beda Gaya Jokowi Bertemu Putin dengan Zelenskyy di https://www.kompas.tv/article/304742/beda-gaya-jokowi-bertemu-putin-dengan-zelenskyy||||"Angkatan bersenjata kami melakukan semua yang mereka bisa," kata Zelenskyy pada konferensi pers di Kyiv.||||Pada kunjungan PM Australia itu juga membawa sejumlah bantuan militer untuk Ukraina senilai USD 100 Juta, dan alat militer. ||||"Australia hari ini akan mengumumkan tambahan 100 juta dolar (AS) dukungan militer, sehingga total pengeluaran kami menjadi hampir 390 juta (AS) dolar. Kami akan memberikan tambahan 14 pengangkut pribadi lapis baja, tambahan 20 Bushmaster - kendaraan mobilitas pelindung yang kami telah menyediakan, sehingga jumlah itu menjadi 60. Kami akan memberikan tambahan peralatan militer lainnya, termasuk drone dan peralatan lain yang telah diminta oleh Ukraina."jelas Anthony dikutip dari Associated Press. ||||Video Editor: Firmansyah|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305540/setelah-jokowi-giliran-pm-australia-anthony-albanese-ke-ukraina
tags: anthony albanese|bantuan militer|pm australia|presiden jokowi|rusia|ukraina|volodymyr zelensky

title: Sekutu Rusia, Presiden Belarus Tuding Ukraina Akan Serang Negaranya
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden Belarusia Alexander Lukashenko mengklaim Ukraina telah mencoba menyerang Belarusia dengan rudal, tetapi gagal, Sabtu (2/7/2022). ||||"Saya harus melaporkan kepada Anda: tiga hari yang lalu, mungkin sedikit lagi, dari wilayah Ukraina mereka mencoba menyerang fasilitas militer di wilayah Belarusia," kata Lukashenko ketika berbicara kepada bangsa, sehari sebelum Hari Kemerdekaan negara itu.||||Lukashenko mengatakan bahwa dia telah memerintahkan pasukan Belarusia untuk menargetkan pusat 'pengambilan keputusan' di Ukraina.||||Baca Juga Putin Ingin Buka Penerbangan Moskwa-Bali, Tertarik? di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305331/putin-ingin-buka-penerbangan-moskwa-bali-tertarik||||Ia juga menegaskan bahwa setiap serangan terhadap Belarus akan memicu tanggapan instan.||||"Kami akan berjuang, saya ulangi, hanya dalam satu kasus, jika Anda melangkahi meter terakhir tanah kami dan menyerang tanah kami. Jika Anda membunuh orang-orang kami, kami akan menjawab. Oleh karena itu, sebagai presiden, saya akan mengatakan jangan sentuh. negara saya, jangan sentuh orang Belarusia saya, jika Anda masih memiliki rasa pertahanan diri."tegas Lukashenko.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305582/sekutu-rusia-presiden-belarus-tuding-ukraina-akan-serang-negaranya
tags: Alexander Lukashenko|belarusia|presiden belarus|presiden ukraina|volodymyr zelensky|belarus|president alexander lukashenko|lukashenko

title: Moving a Light Fixture | Ask This Old House
description: In this video, This Old House master electrician Heath Eastman helps a homeowner with an askew light fixture, centering it over their dining room table.|SUBSCRIBE to This Old House: http://bit.ly/SubscribeThisOldHouse.|Master electrician, Heath Eastman takes us on a house call to help a homeowner move a light over their dining room table. After assessing the situation and getting some careful measurements, the two move the table, shut off the breaker and get to work moving the light fixture.|Difficulty: 2/5|Time: 3 hours|Cost: Under $60|Where to find it?|Heath moves a kitchen ceiling light fixture 12-18 inches to center it over a kitchen table. He uses a small metal rod (about 16 inches long), pushes it through the ceiling, and bends it to a 90-degree angle, so there is about 2 inches of bent wire through the ceiling. Heath says by rotating the rod around 360 degrees without hitting anything, he knows he can freely work in that section of the ceiling.|Once Heath determines that the new location is free of obstacles, he drills a hole using a dust collector, and a 4-inch hole saw. After Heath detaches the fixture, he removes the old electrical box from the ceiling, freeing up the wire. After Heath installs the appropriate junction box and runs the wiring through it, he installs the new light fixture.|Looking for more step by step guidance on how to complete projects around the house? title: Canggih!  Tiongkok Punya Layanan Taksi Self-Driving Tersibuk di Dunia
description: TIONGKOK, KOMPAS, TV - Kini Tiongkok punya taksi pintar.||||Taksi tanpa pengemudi ini memberikan jaminan keselamatan lalu lintas, kemudahan, dan ekonomis untuk para penggunanya.||||Tidak ada seorang pun di belakang kemudi, tetapi taksi ini tahu persis ke mana arah tujuannya.||||Kendaraan bernama Apollo Robotaxi, diproduksi oleh perusahaan teknologi raksasa asal Tiongkok, Baidu yang sebelumnya dikenal sebagai operator mesin pencari.||||Apollo Robotaxi mengangkut pelanggan di sekitar Kota Beijing tanpa pengemudi. Baidu menerima lisensi pertama di Tiongkok pada bulan April lalu untuk mengoperasikan taksi tanpa pengemudi.||||Baidu mengklaim, kendaraan otonomnya dapat membuat mengemudi lebih murah, mudah, dan aman.||||Salah satu pengguna layanan Appolo Robotaxi mengatakan moda transportasi robot ini terasa sedikit lebih aman dibandingkan dengan pengemudi taksi manusia.||||Meski tidak memiliki pengemudi taksi ini memiliki pengawas di kursi penumpang.||||Layanan Appolo Robotaxi kini telah diperluas ke Beijing, Shanghai, dan delapan kota lainnya.||||Apollo go kini telah menyediakan 213.000 perjalanan pada kuartal terakhir tahun lalu,menjadikannya layanan taksi self-driving tersibuk di dunia.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305516/canggih-tiongkok-punya-layanan-taksi-self-driving-tersibuk-di-dunia

title: Russia claims control of Lysychansk, a pivotal city in eastern Ukraine

title: ZUCCHINI AND SAUSAGE PASTA #shorts #asmr
description: This pasta is only one thing....EXCELLENT! Learn how to prepare it with @Rafael Nistor |INGREDIENTS (4 SERVINGS)|320g. Pasta|250g. Pork sausage|120g. Spreadable cheese|4 medium zucchini|Salt and pepper|Extra virgin olive oil|METHOD|Wash the zucchini, cut them in half lengthwise and then in half again into four equal parts. Remove the seeds and then cut them into pieces of the same size. In abundant lightly salted water, cook the zucchini for about 7 min.|In the meantime, take the sausage, remove the casing and cut it slightly into bite-sized pieces. Transfer it into a non-stick pan, divide it into small pieces with a spoon and brown for about 5 min. Then put it aside.|Drain the zucchini in a bowl and add the cream cheese, salt, pepper and oil. With the help of a mini blender, blend to obtain a cream.|In the water where you cooked the zucchini, drop the pasta and cook it until al dente. Drain the pasta in a bowl and add two ladles of cream with the browned sausage. Mix everything well. Ottimo!

title: Adrian Meronk Makes History | Winning Final Round Highlights | 2022 Horizon Irish Open
description: Adrian Meronk made history as the first Polish winner on the DP World Tour after producing fireworks on the back nine to win the 2022 Horizon Irish Open by three shots.|â–º SUBSCRIBE: http://et.golf/Subscribe ||||The DP World Tour lands on Irish shores for the first time this season for the 2022 Horizon Irish Open. Home favourite Shane Lowry will be looking to record his first win since claiming The Open Championship in 2019 and comes into the event in great form, having only missed one cut in his past 14 appearances. The Irishman will be joined by Ryder Cup teammate and World No. 27, Tyrrell Hatton, whose last win on the DP World Tour came at the Abu Dhabi HSBC Championship in January 2021. The Horizon Irish Open will also see Alex Fitzpatrick, younger brother of 2022 U.S. Open champion Matt make his much anticipated professional debut at Mount Juliet Estate. Other notable names to keep an eye on include three-time major winner Padraig Harrington, Ryan Fox and Thomas Pieters who narrowly missed out to Haotong Li in a dramatic play-off at last weekendâ€™s BMW International Open. ||||â–º WEBSITE: http://www.europeantour.com||â–º FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/DPWorldTour||â–º TWITTER https://twitter.com/DPWorldTour||â–º INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/dpworldtour/

title: Laporan Jurnalis Harian Kompas: Korban Terus Berjatuhan, Bangunan Sipil Juga Diserang Rusia
description: KHARKIV, KOMPAS.TV - Perang Rusia-Ukraina terus memanas. Di wilayah timur sekitar perbatasan Rusia Ukraina terus terjadi ledakan.||||Juru Bicara Kementerian Pertahanan Rusia, Igor Konashenkov mengatakan selama tiga hari terakhir pasukan Rusia telah menguasai kilang, tambang, dan pabrik gelatin.||||Pihak Rusia mengklaim ada 190 korban tewas dari pihak Ukraina.||||Sementara itu, Presiden Ukraina, Volodymyr Zelenskyy mengatakan serangan Rusia di wilayah Odesa menghancurkan apartemen dan pemukiman warga sipil.||||Zelenskyy mengatakan setidaknya ada 3 rudal Anti-Kapal KH-22 milik Rusia yang  menghantam sebuah gedung apartemen 9 lantai yang menampung sekitar 160 orang.||||Ukraina mengartikan serangan itu sebagai balasan atas pasukan Rusia yang dipaksa keluar dari Pulau Ular sehari sebelumnya.||Penduduk lokal Kota Serhiivka, Odesa mempertanyakan serangan rudal rusia yang merusak rumah mereka, karena mereka menyatakan bahwa tidak ada personel "militer" atau "separatis" di wilayah itu.||||Kejaksaan Agung Ukraina mencatat setidaknya 2.102 sekolah hancur dan 344 anak tewas di wilayah Ukraina sejak perang meletus pada 24 Februari 2022.||||Rusia telah berulang kali mengklaim bahwa militernya menargetkan situs penyimpanan bahan bakar dan fasilitas militer, bukan daerah pemukiman sipil.||||Meskipun Rudal Rusia baru-baru ini menghantam sebuah gedung apartemen di Kyiv dan sebuah pusat perbelanjaan di pusat Kota Kremenchuk.||||Sementara itu, Badan Pengungsi PBB yaitu UNHCR mencatat lebih dari 5 juta warga Ukraina meninggalkan negaranya dan menjadi pengungsi di beberapa negara Eropa.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305508/laporan-jurnalis-harian-kompas-korban-terus-berjatuhan-bangunan-sipil-juga-diserang-rusia

title: Ducati MotoE: velocitÃ , peso, autonomia. Tutti i numeri della V21L (con Michele Pirro)!
description: Quanto va forte? Quanto pesa? In quanto gira e che autonomia ha? Fin dal primo momento in cui le prima immagini della nuova MotoE targata Ducati sono apparse in rete, la curiositÃ  di tutti gli appassionati ha riguardato questi interrogativi. Ed Ã¨ proprio nel corso di un evento che si Ã¨ tenuto a Modena, nelle scorse ore, che una parte di queste domande ha trovato risposta.|La sigla V21L, tanto per cominciare, Ã¨ quella scelta a Borgo Panigale per identificare la prima moto elettrica Ducati, il prototipo che a partire dal 2023 gareggerÃ  nella World Cup FIM MotoE. La casa di Borgo Panigale sarÃ  partner come fornitore unico con 18 moto in pista nel corso di ogni weekend di gara.|Il progetto MotoE ha rilevanza strategica consentendo di sviluppare competenze per il futuro mantenendo lâ€™approccio che da sempre alimenta lo spirito Ducati: sperimentare soluzioni tecnologiche nel mondo delle competizioni affinchÃ© tutto quello che viene sviluppato possa poi approdare sulle moto destinate agli appassionati.|Ok, direte voi, ma quali sono questi benedetti numeri? Eccoli!|La Ducati MotoE ha un peso totale di 225 kg (12 kg in meno rispetto ai requisiti minimi imposti da Dorna e FIM) e conta su valori di potenza e coppia massime rispettivamente di 150 CV e 140 Nm: al Mugello la moto ha raggiunto i 275 km/h!|Il pacco batteria, lâ€™elemento piÃ¹ vincolante per masse e ingombri, Ã¨ caratterizzato da una sagoma specificatamente pensata per seguire il naturale andamento della zona centrale della moto. Pesa 110 kg e offre una capacitÃ  di 18 kWh con presa di ricarica da 20 kW integrata nel codone.Al suo interno trovano posto 1.152 celle di forma cilindrica del tipo â€œ21700".|Lâ€™inverter, dal peso contenuto di 5 kg, Ã¨ unâ€™unitÃ  derivata da un modello ad alte prestazioni impiegato nelle competizioni automobilistiche per mezzi elettrici, mentre il motore (21 kg di peso e un regime di rotazione massimo di 18.000 giri) Ã¨ stato sviluppato da un partner seguendo le specifiche tecniche fornite da Ducati. Lâ€™intero sistema si basa su una tensione di 800V a pacco batteria completamente carico.|Una delle soluzioni tecniche piÃ¹ avanzate riguarda il sistema di raffreddamento che usa un sofisticato un doppio circuito studiato per rispondere alle differenti esigenze termiche del pacco batteria e del gruppo motore/inverter. CiÃ² garantisce unâ€™estrema regolaritÃ  delle temperature con benefici importanti in termini di costanza delle prestazioni ma anche delle tempistiche di ricarica.|Lâ€™involucro del pacco batteria Ã¨ realizzato in fibra di carbonio e svolge anche la funzione di parte stressata della ciclistica, analogamente a quanto avviene per il motore della Ducati Panigale V4, con un telaio monoscocca Front Frame in alluminio per la zona anteriore dal peso di 3,7 kg.|Il retrotreno Ã¨ composto da un forcellone in alluminio dal peso di 4,8 kg con geometria molto simile a quella della Ducati Desmosedici impegnata in MotoGP. Il telaietto posteriore, che integra codino e sella pilota, Ã¨ realizzato in fibra di carbonio.|Il comparto sospensioni prevede allâ€™avantreno una forcella pressurizzata Ã–hlins NPX 25/30 con steli rovesciati dal diametro di 43 mm derivata dalla Superleggera V4, mentre al retrotreno Ã¨ presente un ammortizzatore Ã–hlins TTX36 completamente regolabile.|Lâ€™impianto frenante Brembo Ã¨ stato dimensionato per le specifiche della Ducati MotoE.Ãˆ composto anteriormente da un doppio disco in acciaio da 338,5 mm di diametro e dallo spessore maggiorato: presenta alettature sul diametro interno per migliorare il raffreddamento ed Ã¨ accoppiato a due pinze GP4RR M4 con pompa radiale.|Al retrotreno la pinza P34 agisce su unâ€™unitÃ  a disco singolo da 220 mm di diametro. Per azionare il freno posteriore Ã¨ possibile utilizzare anche un comando sul manubrio di sinistra.|Lo sviluppo della moto, afferma Ducati, Ã¨ attualmente al 70-75%.|Segui Moto.it su Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/motoit/|e su Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Moto.it|Canale Telegram: https://t.me/+SI91PIKXQSLJtnRw

title: Colbert vs Nyambayar FULL FIGHT: July 3, 2021 | PBC on Showtime
description: (July 3, 2021) Unbeaten rising star Chris â€œPrimetimeâ€ Colbert cruised to a unanimous decision victory over Tugststogt Nyambayar Saturday night to retain his Interim WBA Super Featherweight title in the main event.|The 24-year-old Colbert (16-0, 6 KOs) rode a dominant jab to victory as he landed 112 across the 12 rounds according to CompuBox, buoying a 218 to 78 advantage in punches landed. The Brooklyn-native used the jab to set up a variety of effective power punches that he was able to land from orthodox and southpaw stances. |Mongoliaâ€™s Nyambayar (12-2, 9 KOs), who now fights out of Los Angeles, stepped in to fight Colbert on less than two weeksâ€™ notice, replacing former champion Yuriorkis Gamboa after he suffered a training camp injury. Nyambayar had successful moments in his 130-pound debut, with Colbert even noting the Olympic silver medalistâ€™s power, but he was unable to keep up a sustained attack or keep the busier Colbert from controlling the tempo. |Colbert rode his versatile offensive arsenal to a big advantage on the scorecards and statistically, dominating Nyambayar in punches landed as he connected on 106 power punches to 78 total punches landed by Nyambayar. After 12 rounds, the judges' scores confirmed Colbertâ€™s dominance, as he won the decision with scores of 117-111 and 118-110 twice. |#ChrisColbert #TugststogtNyambayar #ColbertNyambayar|Visit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.||||SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: ||||https://pbcham.ps/FightAlerts||||FOLLOW US:||||https://twitter.com/premierboxing||https://instagram.com/premierboxing||https://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

title: Remaja Nekat Pilih Tabrak Motor Polisi dengan Mobil daripada Ditangkap
description: LAMPUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Kendaraan Personel Polresta Bandar Lampung ditabrak seorang remaja saat melakukan giat rutin maraknya geng motor.||||Peristiwa terjadi saat polisi hendak menertibkan kelompok remaja yang  sedang pesta miras.||||Satu pemuda yang hendak melarikan diri dengan menggunakan mobil  nekat menabrak  motor dinas polisi hingga rusak.||||Peristiwa  terjadi  saat Anggota Polresta Bandar Lampung akan mengamankan sekelompok remaja yang sedang pesta miras di Jl Ahmad Dahlan Pahoman Bandar Lampung.||||Pelaku diamankan di kediamannya pada Sabtu dini hari 2 Juli 2022.||||Pelaku mengaku nekat kabur karena tidak membawa kelengkapan surat kendaraan.||||Saat ini  pelaku bersama delapan rekannya masih menjalani pemeriksaan di Polresta Bandar Lampung. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305514/remaja-nekat-pilih-tabrak-motor-polisi-dengan-mobil-daripada-ditangkap
tags: lampung|operasi miras|polisi ditabrak mobil|remaja tabrak polisi

title: 1955 Arrest Warrant Discovered in Emmett Till Case
description: New evidence has been found in the horrific murder of Black teenager Emmett Till. A team searching the basement of a Mississippi courthouse discovered an arrest warrant from 1955 charging Carolyn Bryant Donham with kidnapping. Donham was the White woman who accused Till of making advances at her, which led to his abduction and brutal murder by two White supremacists. Till's family, who was part of the team that uncovered the warrant, are now calling for her arrest. title: Sang-e-Mah Last EP 26 [ğ‚ğ‚] 3rd July 22 - Presented by Dawlance, Itel Mobile, Master Paints
description: https://bit.ly/Humtvpk Subscribe To HUM TVâ€™s YouTube Channel! |Sang-e-Mah Last EP 26 [ğ‚ğ‚] 3rd July 22 - Presented by Dawlance, Itel Mobile, Master Paints|Presented By Dawlance DawlanceReliableHai & Itel Mobile EnjoyBetterLife |Powered By Master Paints MasterPaints|The second part of a trilogy whoâ€™s first part is one of the most splendidly articulated, absorbing and riveting dramas, Pakistanâ€™s history has ever seen â€“ Sang E Mar Mar, HUM TV brings to you Sang E Mah. |In the words of the gifted writer of Aseerzadi, Ehd E Wafa and Sang E Mar Mar, Mustafa Afridi, directed by the brilliant Saife Hassan whoâ€™s work Bari Aapa,  Ehd E Wafa and Ru Baru speak volumes of just how accomplished he is as a director and produced by none other than the finest in Pakistan, Momina Duraid. | |â€˜Gaghâ€™ a Pashto word that translates to ailan or proclamation, even though illegal is an ongoing kabayali pathan rasm through which marriage is enforced by firing at a girlâ€™s home. |Sang E Mah revolves around the concept of gagh and encompasses the enactment of law to combat this tradition. |Along with highlighting gagh, the tale of Sang E Mah comprises of a transcendent tale of love, and retribution between a father and son. |There are three similarities between Sang E Mar Mar and Sang E Mah, some of the far famed cast members such as Nauman Ejaz and Sania Saeed graced both parts with their incomparable acting, both dramas are based on kabayali pathan tradition and both meticulously encompass the undeniable subjugation and oppression of women in rural areas.|The Cast |Other than the powerful and compelling story of Sang E Mah,  prodigious director, splendid writer and  profound production, what makes Sang E Mah a drama unlike any other is its highly skilled and exceptional cast. The drama features Nauman Ijaz, Samiya Mumtaz, Sania Saeed, Omair Rana, Hania Aamir, Kubra Khan, Zaviyar Ejaz, Hasan Noman, Najiba Faiz and for the first time ever the legendary Atif Aslam. |Conclusion |Sang E Mah exhibits diversity unlike any other Pakistani drama before. Different cultures, sects and religions are all part of this dynamic drama serial.|Writer: Mustafa Afridi |Director: Saife Hassan |Producer: Momina Duraid |CAST :|Atif Aslam|Nauman Ijaz|Samiya Mumtaz|Sania Saeed|Omair Rana|Hania Aamir|Kubra Khan|Zaviyar Ejaz|Hasan Noman|Najiba Faiz|#SangeMah_LastEP26|#HUMTV|#HumDRAMA

title: Arson at an Abortion Clinic Foreshadows a Post-Roe Future
description: Roe V. Wade being overturned is not the first obstacle for this independent abortion clinic in Wyoming. An arsonist lit Wellspring Access Health on fire last month, just weeks before they were set to open. Now, Roe V. Wade has been overturned and their clinic is in a state that plans to ban abortions except for certain cases. title: Japanese Latter-day Saints Build Temple
description: Latter-day Saints in Japan are reflecting on the history of the first temple of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints in Asia. |The Tokyo Japan Temple, which first opened in 1980, will reopen in July following an extensive renovation that started in September 2017. |Temples are sacred spaces for members of the Church. They are considered houses of God, places of holiness and peace separate from the preoccupations of the world. |Temples provide a place where Church members make formal promises and commitments to God. They are also places where the highest sacraments of the faith occur â€” the marriage of couples and the â€œsealingâ€ of families for eternity.|Whenever The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints constructs a new temple, a dedication ceremony is held when the building is finished. Before the temple is dedicated, an open house is often held for the general public. After the temple is formally dedicated, entrance is reserved for faithful members of the Church.
tags: Christian Temple|The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints

title: HOW HARD CAN I RIDE A WOODEN BIKE UNTIL IT SNAPS?
description: How hard can I ride a wooden bike until it snaps? I challenge myself to land some big tricks on my custom wooden mountain bike on a BMX race track with rollers and jumps before hitting a skatepark! But how long will it last? |Today I woke up and decided that my wooden bike needed to be ridden super hard and pushed to the limits of what is capable on a bicycle made of wood so I took it to the lovely Braintree BMX race track to use on some of the jumps and rollers as a good start to the video and to get the bike warmed up! After some big moves disaster struck and with the bike in pieces (it snapped) we needed an idea so operation fix wooden bike was formed. We raced home via a big field for drifting in my V8 truck in before coming back home and making the best modification to the bike yet. After some skillful fixing the bike was back up and running and I still had a challenge left to perform, the tailwhip! But was it possible!?  |I hope you enjoy the video!||||MERCH:||https://www.tothesky.store/||||----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------||||Welcome to my channel, I'm a professional Freeride Mountain biker and former FMB world champion(2013).  ||||This channel is all about Mountain biking, I make a huge variety of videos for everyone who loves dirt: From downhill biking to slower paced trials riding and everything in between like dirt jumping, slopestyle and enduro!  ||||As well as making entertaining videos(I hope) I also like to help YOU out too, with videos such as:  ||- How to ride better ||- Trick tips and How to's ||- Travel VLOGS ||- GoPro camera tips ||- In-depth entertaining features ||- POV craziness ||- Funny videos |||| I also try to reply to everyone so leave some comments too!

title: El Salvador women jailed for suffering miscarriages - BBC News
description: El Salvador has seen several high profile cases of women who suffered miscarriages being sentenced to 30 years in jail for murder.|In February, four of these women sat down before the the press. Between them, they had served nearly 50 years in prison.|Among them was Elsy. who told the BBC: "I just kept thinking, 'Why? Why did those who testified against me do this?'"|The country has some of the world's harshest anti-abortion laws, which ban all kinds of terminations even if the pregnancy poses a risk to the mother's life or results from rape or incest.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#ElSalvador #BBCNews

title: Why Pharmaceuticals Are So Complicated In The U.S. | CNBC Marathon
description: CNBC Marathon explores why pharmaceuticals are so complicated in the United States.|Concerns over prescription drug prices have grown into a big political issue, with nearly one in four Americans saying it's difficult to afford their medications, according to a March 2019 poll by the Kaiser Family Foundation. Pharmacies technically set their own prices for generic drugs, but there are other players involved that complicate the process.|Johnson & Johnson, the biggest pharmaceutical company in the U.S. based on market cap, announced in November 2021 it plans to spin off its consumer business into a new publicly traded company by November 2023. Analysts overwhelmingly say itâ€™s a smart business move, but it could also come with some risks.|Meanwhile, the U.S.'s approval of Biogen's Alzheimer's drug Aduhelm was heralded as a historic triumph in the fight against the memory-robbing disease. But so far, Biogen has reported only a fraction of Aduhelm revenue to meet Wall Street's expectations. Patients and physicians have been torn over the drug's murky clinical data and its high price tag. Aduhelm's lackluster launch has been costly, forcing Biogen to take measures to keep the drug afloat.|For Covid-19 vaccine maker, BioNTech, they had little recognition outside of their hometown of Germany prior to the pandemic. Over a month and a half before the World Health Organization officially declared a pandemic, BioNTech CEO UÄŸur Åahin met with his wife, BioNTechâ€™s co-founder and chief medical officer Ã–zlem TÃ¼reci, and together they agreed to redirect most of the companyâ€™s resources to developing a vaccine. The founders were confident in the potential of their mRNA technology, which they knew could trigger a powerful immune response. That confidence wasnâ€™t necessarily shared by the broader medical community. No mRNA vaccine or treatment had ever been approved before. But the coupleâ€™s timely breakthrough was actually decades in the making.|CNBC Marathon brings together the best of CNBC on YouTube.|Chapters:|00:00 Introduction|00:31 Why U.S. pharmacies overcharge (Published August 2021)|16:35 The rise of BioNTech (Published October 2021)|34:21 Why the biggest pharma company in the U.S. is breaking up (Published January 2022)|45:42 Whatâ€™s the controversy behind Biogenâ€™s Alzheimerâ€™s drug? title: Jammu villagers overpower two 'most-wanted' Lashkar terrorists; Lt Guv, police announce cash reward
description: Two heavy armed Lashkar-e-Toiba terrorists were overpowered by villagers and handed to the police in Jammu and Kashmir's Reasi district, the J&K Police said. Lashkar commander Talib Hussain, a mastermind behind the recent IED blasts in the Reasi district, was nabbed by the security forces in Tuksan after being overpowered by the villagers. The J&K Police had declared a bounty on the LeT commander. Another terrorist Faizal Ahmed Dar, was also arrested in the village. Watch this video to know more.|#JammuAndKashmir #LashkarEToiba #Terrorists #Reasi #IEDBlasts #TalibHussain #FaizalAhmedDar

title: Pemuda Usia 23 Tahun Gembala Ribuan Bebek Antarkota, Raih Rp40 Juta Setiap 5 Bulan Sekali!
description: MADIUN, KOMPAS.TV - Musim panen padi di Kabupaten Madiun, Jawa Timur dimanfaatkan seorang pemuda asal Ngawi, untuk menggembala ribuan bebek peliharaannya.||||Dengan melepas bebek ke areal persawahan yang baru dipanen.||||Penggembala bebek ini, mampu meraup untung hingga puluhan juta rupiah.||||Hari masih pagi, namun ribuan bebek ini sudah diangkut pemiliknya menggunakan kendaraan pikap.||||Bukan ke pasar unggas, tetapi mobil berhenti di areal persawahan Desa Balerejo, Kecamatan Balerejo, Kabupaten Madiun, Jawa Timur.||||Rupanya ribuan bebek petelur ini milik Revi Nurkasandi, pemuda berusia 23 tahun warga Kecamatan Paron, Kabupaten Ngawi.||||Baca Juga 24.000 Hewan Kurban di Kabupaten Banjar Bebas PMK, Dinas Peternakan Imbau Tak Khawatir di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305257/24-000-hewan-kurban-di-kabupaten-banjar-bebas-pmk-dinas-peternakan-imbau-tak-khawatir||||Ribuan bebek dia bawa jauh-jauh dari Ngawi bersama satu orang teman, untuk di gembala di areal persawahan yang baru saja selesai dipanen.||||Dengan membawa sebatang bambu yang diberi plastik merah di ujungnya, bebek - bebek ini diarahkan ke sawah yang banyak terdapat makanan seperti cacing, keong, sisa gabah dan sebagainya.||||Tanpa lama, bebek bebek ini pun langsung menyerbu ke tempat sasaran.||||Profesi sebagai penggembala bebek telah dilakoni sejak 10 tahun lalu.||||Dirinya memilih melepaskan bebek ke sawah, karena bebek dapat secara langsung mencari pakan sendiri dan yang pasti dapat menghemat pengeluaran untuk membeli pakan unggas bebek.||||Tak hanya sampai kabupaten Madiun saja.||||Di hari lain, dirinya juga menggembala bebek peliharaan hingga ke Kabupaten Magetan dan Kabupaten Ponorogo.||||Setiap 5 bulan sekali, bebek-bebek ini akan dikirim ke tempat pengembangbiakan di Kabupaten Blitar.||||Setiap lima bulan sekali itu juga, dirinya bisa mendapatkan honor bagi hasil dari mitra sebesar Rp40 juta.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305435/pemuda-usia-23-tahun-gembala-ribuan-bebek-antarkota-raih-rp40-juta-setiap-5-bulan-sekali

title: Russia, Ukraine claim control of Lysychansk as fighting rages on | DW News
description: In Ukraine, intense fighting is raging for control of the city of Lysychansk. It is the last stronghold of Ukrainian resistance in Luhansk province in the east. After weeks of clashes, Lysychansk is now the subject of competing claims. title: 2022 Dodge Charger Jailbreak vs CT5-V Blackwing vs Lexus IS 500 // With CHRIS HARRIS + DRAG RACE
description: The 2022 Dodge Charger Jailbreak ($106,810 in Canada, $87,595 in the US), the 2022 Cadillac CT5-V Blackwing ($87,798, $83,995) and the 2022 Lexus IS500 ($77,650, $67,400) are prepped and ready for a day at the Throttle House test track - with special guest Chris Harris! Since he has never been behind the wheel of a Hellcat, it seems fitting that he will be championing the Jailbreak. Thomas is in the only available manual of the group, the supercharged CT5-V Blackwing, and James is representing snarling naturally aspirated V8s with the Lexus IS500. Watch as the guys drag race, track test, and get a little sideways in these three endangered species of motor vehicle. We hope you enjoy this very special episode! Thanks for watching! SUBSCRIBE!|A huge thank you to Matt for lending us his Blackwing, Dave for driving it out, and Val, Shawn, Matt and the entire Leggat team for saving the day.|And to Downsview Place Auto Group for their Dodge Charger SRT Hellcat Redeye Widebody Jailbreak|And to Chris, Edward, Cliff and the Collecting Cars team for joining in on the fun.|And to Jeremy Tedes, for his continued unwavering support of our adventures.|And to Michelin Canada, for replacing tires. title: China's new target in the battle to control the Pacific | 60 Minutes Australia
description: Subscribe here: http://9Soci.al/chmP50wA97J Full Episodes: https://9now.app.link/uNP4qBkmN6 | Too Close to Home (2022)|At its closest point the distance between Australia and the Solomon Islands is just under two thousand kilometres. Being so near is why Canberra is so worried about the deals the small Pacific nation is signing with China. It means the once inconceivable idea of a Chinese military base being built right on our doorstep has become a very real possibility. And now thereâ€™s another potential threat that must be considered - Beijing is also cosying up to Papua New Guinea, a country of immense strategic significance. title: Nasib 46 Jemaah Calon Haji dengan Visa Palsu yang Akhirnya Resmi Dipulangkan
description: KOMPAS.TV - Jemaah akan menjalani Wukuf di Arafah, Muzdalifah dan Mina pada tanggal 9 Dzulhijjah atau Jumat 8 Juli 2022.||||Jemaah yang tiba di Bandara King Abdul Aziz, Jeddah Arab Saudi, langsung menuju Mekkah untuk menunaikan Umrah Wajib.||||Jemaah yang tiba sudah mengenakan kain ihram dan mengambil miqat di embarkasi.||||Baca Juga Pemberangkatan Kloter Terakhir Jemaah Calon Haji, 8 Jemaah Surabaya Gagal Naik Haji Akibat Sakit! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/305434/pemberangkatan-kloter-terakhir-jemaah-calon-haji-8-jemaah-surabaya-gagal-naik-haji-akibat-sakit||||Hingga Minggu 3 Juli 2022 lebih dari 91.000 jemaah Indonesia yang tiba di tanah suci.||||Sisanya tiba secara bertahap, hingga batas akhir masuk Mekkah pada Minggu 3 Juli 2022.||||Sementara itu, 46 jemaah calon haji non kuota asal Indonesia dipulangkan oleh pemerintah Arab Saudi.||||Jemaah calon haji itu dipulangkan karena masuk Arab Saudi bukan dengan visa haji resmi Arab Saudi untuk Indonesia. |||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/305453/nasib-46-jemaah-calon-haji-dengan-visa-palsu-yang-akhirnya-resmi-dipulangkan
